      "body_html": "<!-- Meta Description for SEO --><!-- Product Title --><!-- Short Description -->\n<p>Bring home the luxurious taste and aroma of Kashmir with our pure Mongra saffron. Hand-harvested from Pampore’s saffron fields, these deep crimson threads are naturally dried and carefully packed—ideal for cooking, wellness, and gifting.</p>\n<!-- Full Description -->\n<h4>About the Product</h4>\n<p>At Kashmir Online Store, we bring you the finest Kashmiri Mongra Saffron, known for its <em>deep red color</em>, <em>bold flavor</em>, and <em>rich aroma</em>. Grown in the pristine valleys of Pampore, this saffron is carefully harvested by hand and sun-dried to retain its natural potency. Ideal for everything from royal biryanis to Ayurvedic skincare.</p>\n<!-- Product Details Table -->\n<h3>Product Details</h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Feature</th>\n<th>Details</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Type</td>\n<td>Kashmiri Mongra Saffron</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Harvest Location</td>\n<td>Pampore, Kashmir</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Color</td>\n<td>Deep Crimson Red</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Aroma</td>\n<td>Strong, Earthy, Floral</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Flavor Profile</td>\n<td>Rich, Slightly Bitter-Sweet</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Drying Process</td>\n<td>Traditional Sun-Dried</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Purity</td>\n<td>100% Pure – No Additives</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Farming Method</td>\n<td>Naturally Grown, Chemical-Free</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Shelf Life</td>\n<td>24 Months</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Storage</td>\n<td>Cool, dark, dry place</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Packaging</td>\n<td>Glass Jar / Vacuum-Sealed Pouch</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- Pack Sizes -->\n<h3>Available Sizes</h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Pack Size</th>\n<th>Recommended Use</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1 gram</td>\n<td>Light culinary use, saffron tea, gifting</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2 grams</td>\n<td>Regular cooking &amp; wellness use</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5 grams</td>\n<td>Gifting, skincare, large meal prep</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10 grams</td>\n<td>Frequent use or family-size pack</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><em>*Bulk orders and custom packaging available upon request.</em></p>\n<!-- Usage Guide -->\n<h2>Usage Guide – How to Use Kashmiri Saffron</h2>\n<h3>1. Soaking Method (Recommended)</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Take 5–6 saffron strands</li>\n<li>Place them in 2 tablespoons of warm water or milk</li>\n<li>Let soak for 15–20 minutes</li>\n<li>Add both strands and infused liquid to your recipe</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong> Soaking helps release color (crocin), aroma (safranal), and flavor (picrocrocin).</p>\n<h3>2. Culinary Uses</h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Dish</th>\n<th>Usage</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Biryani &amp; Pulao</td>\n<td>Add infused saffron while cooking rice</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Indian Desserts</td>\n<td>Mix into kheer, phirni, or sweets</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Saffron Milk</td>\n<td>Stir into warm milk with sugar or cardamom</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Kahwa / Tea</td>\n<td>Add to hot tea with cinnamon and almonds</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Baked Goods</td>\n<td>Infuse in milk before adding to batter</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>3. Wellness &amp; Skincare Uses</h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Application</th>\n<th>Instructions</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Immunity Drink</td>\n<td>Mix saffron with honey, turmeric, and warm milk</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Skincare Mask</td>\n<td>Crush strands and blend with rosewater or milk</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Mood Tea</td>\n<td>Brew saffron with lemon, honey, and warm water</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>Storage Tips</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Keep saffron in an airtight container</li>\n<li>Store in a cool, dark place away from sunlight</li>\n<li>Do not refrigerate</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- Store Benefits -->\n<h2>Why Choose Kashmir Online Store?</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Direct sourcing from local Kashmiri farmers</li>\n<li>Zero additives, preservatives, or colorants</li>\n<li>Always fresh, seasonally harvested batches</li>\n<li>Fast, secure packaging and doorstep delivery</li>\n<li>Trusted by saffron buyers across India and globally</li>\n</ul>",
