      "body_html": "<style>\n    body {\n      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      padding: 20px;\n      background-color: #fff;\n      color: #333;\n    }\n    h1, h2, h3 {\n      color: #2E8B57; /* green */\n    }\n    .feature-badges {\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n    .badge {\n      display: inline-block;\n      background-color: #d4edda;\n      color: #155724;\n      font-weight: bold;\n      padding: 5px 10px;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      margin-right: 8px;\n      font-size: 14px;\n    }\n    .badge.vegan {\n      background-color: #98FB98;\n    }\n    .badge.gluten-free {\n      background-color: #90EE90;\n    }\n    .badge.organic {\n      background-color: #228B22;\n      color: #fff;\n    }\n    .stock-status {\n      background-color: #32CD32;\n      color: #fff;\n      padding: 10px;\n      font-weight: bold;\n      border-radius: 8px;\n      margin-bottom: 20px;\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n    .highlight-box {\n      background-color: #f0fff0;\n      border-left: 5px solid #2E8B57;\n      padding: 10px;\n      margin: 20px 0;\n      font-size: 16px;\n    }\n    ul, ol {\n      margin-left: 20px;\n    }\n    table {\n      border-collapse: collapse;\n      width: 100%;\n      margin-bottom: 30px;\n    }\n    table, th, td {\n      border: 1px solid #ccc;\n    }\n    th {\n      background-color: #e6f5e6;\n      color: #2E8B57;\n      text-align: left;\n      padding: 8px;\n    }\n    td {\n      padding: 8px;\n    }\n  </style>\n<h1>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"> <br>\n</h1>\n<div class=\"feature-badges\">\n<span class=\"badge vegan\">Vegan</span> <span class=\"badge gluten-free\">Gluten-Free</span> <span class=\"badge organic\">100% Organic</span> <span class=\"badge\">No Added Sugar</span> <span class=\"badge\"><br></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"stock-status\">In Stock - Premium Quality Guaranteed!</div>\n<h2>Product Overview</h2>\n<p>Experience the luxury of authentic Kashmir saffron with our premium grade threads. Hand-picked from the pristine valleys of Kashmir, each strand delivers exceptional aroma, color, and flavor that transforms your culinary creations into gourmet masterpieces.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-box\">\n<strong>Discount Code:</strong> Use code <strong>KOS150</strong> to get 10% off all prepaid orders!</div>\n<h2>Key Features &amp; Benefits</h2>\n<h3>Premium Quality Assurance</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Grade A+ Kashmir Saffron</strong> - Highest quality threads with deep red color</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Hand-Picked &amp; Sun-Dried</strong> - Traditional harvesting methods preserved</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Lab Tested for Purity</strong> - No artificial colors, preservatives, or additives</li>\n<li>\n<strong>ISO 22000 Certified</strong> - International food safety standards maintained</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Culinary Excellence</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Intense Aroma</strong> - Rich, honey-like fragrance that enhances any dish</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Vibrant Color</strong> - Natural golden-yellow hue for beautiful presentation</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Distinctive Flavor</strong> - Sweet, metallic taste with hay-like notes</li>\n<li>\n<strong>High Crocin Content</strong> - Superior coloring strength (&gt;250)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Product Specifications</h2>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Specification</th>\n<th>Details</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Product Name</strong></td>\n<td>Premium Kashmir Saffron Threads</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Net Weight</strong></td>\n<td>1 gram (approximately 450-500 threads)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Origin</strong></td>\n<td>Kashmir Valley, India</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Grade</strong></td>\n<td>Mongra Grade (Premium)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Moisture Content</strong></td>\n<td>≤ 12%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Crocin Level</strong></td>\n<td>≥ 250 (High Coloring Strength)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Safranal Content</strong></td>\n<td>≥ 30 (Aroma Compound)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Picrocrocin</strong></td>\n<td>≥ 70 (Flavor Compound)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Shelf Life</strong></td>\n<td>3 years from manufacturing date</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Storage</strong></td>\n<td>Cool, dry place away from direct sunlight</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Packaging</strong></td>\n<td>Air-tight container with tamper-proof seal</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2>Usage Instructions &amp; Serving Suggestions</h2>\n<h3>How to Use</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<strong>Soaking Method:</strong> Soak 8-10 threads in 2 tablespoons of warm milk or water for 10-15 minutes</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Direct Addition:</strong> Add threads directly to hot dishes during cooking</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Grinding:</strong> Crush threads with mortar and pestle for powder form</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Blooming:</strong> Heat threads in dry pan for 30 seconds before use for enhanced aroma</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Perfect for These Dishes</h3>\n<div class=\"ingredients-grid\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<h5>Sweet Dishes</h5>\n<p>Kheer, Kulfi, Halwa, Ice Cream, Cakes</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<h5>Savory Dishes</h5>\n<p>Biryani, Pulao, Curry, Paella</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<h5>Beverages</h5>\n<p>Tea, Milk, Lassi, Cocktails</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<h5>International</h5>\n<p>Risotto, Bouillabaisse, Saffron Bread</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2>Nutritional Facts &amp; Information</h2>\n<h3>Nutritional Content per 1 gram (serving size)</h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Nutrient</th>\n<th>Amount per 1g</th>\n<th>% Daily Value*</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Calories</strong></td>\n<td>3.1 kcal</td>\n<td>0.15%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Total Carbohydrates</strong></td>\n<td>0.65g</td>\n<td>0.2%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Dietary Fiber</strong></td>\n<td>0.04g</td>\n<td>0.1%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Sugars</strong></td>\n<td>0g</td>\n<td>0%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Protein</strong></td>\n<td>0.11g</td>\n<td>0.2%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Total Fat</strong></td>\n<td>0.06g</td>\n<td>0.1%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Saturated Fat</strong></td>\n<td>0.02g</td>\n<td>0.1%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Sodium</strong></td>\n<td>1.5mg</td>\n<td>0.06%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Potassium</strong></td>\n<td>17.2mg</td>\n<td>0.4%</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>Key Vitamins &amp; Minerals</h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Vitamin/Mineral</th>\n<th>Amount per 1g</th>\n<th>Benefits</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Vitamin C</strong></td>\n<td>0.8mg</td>\n<td>Antioxidant support, immune system</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Vitamin A</strong></td>\n<td>5.3 IU</td>\n<td>Eye health, skin health</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Folate</strong></td>\n<td>0.9mcg</td>\n<td>Cell division, DNA synthesis</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Riboflavin (B2)</strong></td>\n<td>0.003mg</td>\n<td>Energy metabolism</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Niacin (B3)</strong></td>\n<td>0.015mg</td>\n<td>Nervous system function</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Iron</strong></td>\n<td>0.11mg</td>\n<td>Blood formation, oxygen transport</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Manganese</strong></td>\n<td>0.28mg</td>\n<td>Bone health, wound healing</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Copper</strong></td>\n<td>0.003mg</td>\n<td>Iron absorption, connective tissue</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Magnesium</strong></td>\n<td>2.6mg</td>\n<td>Muscle function, bone health</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Phosphorus</strong></td>\n<td>2.5mg</td>\n<td>Bone and teeth health</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>Bioactive Compounds</h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Compound</th>\n<th>Concentration</th>\n<th>Health Benefits</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Crocin</strong></td>\n<td>≥ 250 units</td>\n<td>Antioxidant, anti-inflammatory, mood support</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Safranal</strong></td>\n<td>≥ 30 units</td>\n<td>Neuroprotective, antimicrobial properties</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Picrocrocin</strong></td>\n<td>≥ 70 units</td>\n<td>Digestive support, appetite stimulant</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Crocetin</strong></td>\n<td>High levels</td>\n<td>Cardiovascular support, eye health</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Kaempferol</strong></td>\n<td>Present</td>\n<td>Anti-inflammatory, antioxidant</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"highlight-box\">\n<h4>💡 Nutritional Highlights</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Zero Added Sugar:</strong> Naturally sugar-free spice</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Low Calorie:</strong> Only 3.1 calories per gram</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Rich in Antioxidants:</strong> High levels of crocin and safranal</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Mineral Dense:</strong> Good source of manganese and potassium</li>\n<li>\n<strong>No Artificial Additives:</strong> 100% pure saffron threads</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h4>*Daily Values &amp; Usage Notes</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>*Percent Daily Values are based on a 2,000 calorie diet</li>\n<li>Typical serving size: 0.1g (8-10 threads) for 4-6 portions</li>\n<li>Values may vary slightly based on harvest season and storage conditions</li>\n<li>Nutritional analysis conducted by NABL accredited laboratory</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Health Benefits</h2>\n<h3>Nutritional Properties</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Antioxidant Rich</strong> - High levels of crocin and safranal protect cells</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Mood Enhancer</strong> - Natural compounds may help improve mood</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Digestive Aid</strong> - Traditional use for digestive wellness</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Anti-inflammatory</strong> - Natural compounds with anti-inflammatory properties</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Heart Health</strong> - May support cardiovascular wellness</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Traditional Ayurvedic Uses</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Supports healthy skin complexion</li>\n<li>Promotes restful sleep when used in warm milk</li>\n<li>Traditional remedy for respiratory wellness</li>\n<li>Used in Ayurvedic formulations for vitality</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Storage &amp; Care Instructions</h2>\n<h4>Proper Storage</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Store in original air-tight container</li>\n<li>Keep in cool, dry place (below 25°C)</li>\n<li>Protect from direct sunlight and moisture</li>\n<li>Do not refrigerate - room temperature is ideal</li>\n<li>Use clean, dry spoon when handling</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Signs of Quality</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Color:</strong> Deep red threads with slight orange tips</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Aroma:</strong> Strong, sweet, hay-like fragrance</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Texture:</strong> Dry, brittle threads that break easily</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Water Test:</strong> Should release golden-yellow color in warm water</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Certifications &amp; Quality Assurance</h2>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Certification</th>\n<th>Details</th>\n<th>License/Certificate Number</th>\n<th>Validity</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>FSSAI Approved</strong></td>\n<td>Food Safety and Standards Authority of India</td>\n<td><strong>11022470000118</strong></td>\n<td>Current &amp; Valid</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"highlight-box\">\n<h4>🏆 Quality Guarantee</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Government Approved:</strong> Licensed by FSSAI for food safety compliance</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Regular Inspections:</strong> Facility inspected and approved by food safety authorities</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Quality Standards:</strong> Meets all Indian food safety and quality standards</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Consumer Protection:</strong> Full compliance with food safety regulations</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2>Package Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>1g Premium Kashmir Saffron Threads</li>\n<li>Air-tight storage container</li>\n<li>Authenticity certificate</li>\n<li>Recipe booklet with 10 traditional recipes</li>\n<li>Usage guide and tips</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h4>How much saffron should I use per serving?</h4>\n<p>Use 8-10 threads (approximately 0.1g) for 4-6 servings. A little goes a long way!</p>\n<h4>How can I verify the authenticity?</h4>\n<p>Authentic saffron will release golden-yellow color in warm water and have a distinctive sweet aroma. Avoid if it releases red color immediately.</p>\n<h4>Can I use this for skincare?</h4>\n<p>Yes, saffron is traditionally used in face masks. Mix a few threads with milk or honey for natural skincare benefits.</p>\n<h4>What's the difference between grades?</h4>\n<p>Mongra grade (our product) is the highest quality with deep red color and maximum flavor. Lower grades may have more yellow parts mixed in.</p>\n<h2>Customer Reviews Highlights</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-box\">\n<h5>Quality Testimonials</h5>\n<p><em>\"Absolutely authentic! The aroma hit me as soon as I opened the package. Perfect for my biryanis and desserts. Worth every penny!\"</em> - Verified Purchase</p>\n<p><em>\"Direct from Kashmir - you can taste the difference. Best saffron I've purchased online.\"</em> - Verified Purchase</p>\n</div>\n<h2>Safety Information &amp; Allergens</h2>\n<div class=\"warning-box\">\n<h4>⚠️ Important Safety Information</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Pregnancy:</strong> Consult healthcare provider before use during pregnancy</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Dosage:</strong> Do not exceed 5g per day for adults</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Allergies:</strong> Rare but possible - discontinue if any allergic reaction occurs</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Medication:</strong> Consult doctor if taking blood pressure medications</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Children:</strong> Use in moderation for children under 12</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h3>Allergen Information</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>✅ Gluten-Free</li>\n<li>✅ Dairy-Free</li>\n<li>✅ Nut-Free</li>\n<li>✅ Soy-Free</li>\n<li>✅ Vegan &amp; Vegetarian Friendly</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Brand Story &amp; Sourcing</h2>\n<p>Our saffron comes directly from small-scale farmers in the Kashmir Valley who have been cultivating this precious spice for generations. We ensure fair trade practices and support sustainable farming methods that preserve both the environment and traditional cultivation techniques.</p>\n<h3>Our Commitment</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Direct Source:</strong> No middlemen - straight from Kashmir farms</li>\n<li>\n<strong