      "body_html": "<div style=\"font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: #222; line-height: 1.6; padding: 16px; max-width: 800px; margin: auto;\">\n<!-- Intro -->\n<h3 style=\"font-size: 22px; color: #2e7d32; margin-bottom: 12px;\">Pure Kashmiri Saffron &amp; Spices – Trusted by Thousands</h3>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">Discover premium saffron, herbs, and spices sourced directly from the valleys of Kashmir. Whether for wellness, cooking, or gifting, Kashmir Online Store brings you purity you can taste.</p>\n<!-- Highlights -->\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #388e3c; margin-bottom: 10px;\">Why You'll Love It</h4>\n<ul style=\"list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">✔️ <strong style=\"color: #2e7d32;\">100% Natural &amp; Pure:</strong> No additives or preservatives.</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">✔️ <strong style=\"color: #2e7d32;\">Available Forms:</strong> Powder, Whole, Dried Threads</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">✔️ <strong style=\"color: #2e7d32;\">Lab-Tested:</strong> Each batch is tested for purity and safety.</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">✔️ <strong style=\"color: #2e7d32;\">Pregnancy Safe:</strong> Trusted by expecting mothers (see below)</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">✔️ <strong style=\"color: #2e7d32;\">Free Delivery:</strong> Fast, trackable shipping across India</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- Pregnancy Use -->\n<div style=\"background-color: #f1f8e9; padding: 16px; border-left: 5px solid #66BB6A; margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n<h4 style=\"color: #2e7d32; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 0;\">Safe During Pregnancy</h4>\n<p>Kashmiri saffron is known for its gentle support during pregnancy. It may help with digestion, stress relief, and mood balance.</p>\n<ul style=\"padding-left: 18px;\">\n<li>🌸 Relieves mood swings and fatigue</li>\n<li>🌸 Traditionally mixed in warm milk for prenatal health</li>\n<li>🌸 Easy to digest &amp; caffeine-free</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #777;\"><em>Always consult your doctor before use during pregnancy.</em></p>\n</div>\n<!-- Certification Section -->\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #388e3c; margin-bottom: 10px;\">Certifications &amp; Quality Assurance</h4>\n<ul style=\"list-style: none; padding-left: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">🔬 <strong>FSSAI Certified</strong> – Food safety approved</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">📄 <strong>Lab-Tested</strong> – For color, aroma, &amp; microbial safety</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">🌱 <strong>Non-GMO</strong> &amp; <strong>Vegan</strong> friendly</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">🌿 <strong>Gluten-Free</strong> &amp; <strong>Preservative-Free</strong>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- Expiry Info -->\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #388e3c; margin-bottom: 10px;\">Shelf Life &amp; Storage</h4>\n<ul style=\"list-style: none; padding-left: 0; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">📅 <strong>Expiry:</strong> Best before 24 months from packaging</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">🏠 <strong>Storage:</strong> Keep in a cool, dry place away from sunlight</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">🧊 <strong>Tip:</strong> Store in an airtight jar to retain aroma &amp; color</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- Specifications Table -->\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #388e3c; margin-bottom: 10px;\">Product Specifications</h4>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"background-color: #e8f5e9;\">\n<th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #C8E6C9;\">Attribute</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #C8E6C9;\">Details</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;\">Form</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;\">Powder, Whole, Dried Threads</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background-color: #f9f9f9;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;\">Weight Options</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;\">Under 1g to 50g+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;\">Price Range</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;\">₹499 – ₹3,500+</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background-color: #f9f9f9;\">\n<td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;\">Delivery</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;\">Free shipping across India</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;\">Best Use</td>\n<td style=\"padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;\">Cooking, Gifting, Pregnancy, Wellness</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<!-- Returns -->\n<h4 style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #388e3c; margin-top: 28px;\">Returns &amp; Customer Support</h4>\n<ul style=\"list-style: none; padding-left: 0;\">\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">🔁 <strong>30-Day Return Policy</strong> – No questions asked</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">📞 <strong>Friendly Support</strong> – Available via WhatsApp &amp; Email</li>\n<li style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">💬 <strong>Real-Time Order Tracking</strong> – Stay updated at every step</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- Final CTA -->\n<p style=\"font-size: 15px; margin-top: 24px; color: #444;\">Add authentic Kashmiri richness to your kitchen with <strong style=\"color: #1b5e20;\">Kashmir Online Store</strong>. Quality you can trust. Wellness you can feel.</p>\n</div>\n<!-- Contact Info -->\n<div style=\"margin-top: 30px; background-color: #e8f5e9; padding: 16px; border-left: 4px solid #66BB6A;\">\n<h4 style=\"color: #2e7d32; margin-top: 0;\">Need Help or Have Questions?</h4>\n<p style=\"margin: 6px 0; font-size: 15px;\">📧 Email us at: <a style=\"color: #1b5e20; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"mailto:contact@kashmironlinestore.com\"> contact@kashmironlinestore.com </a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 6px 0; font-size: 15px;\">📞 Call or WhatsApp: <a style=\"color: #1b5e20; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"tel:+918899937924\"> +91 88999 37924 </a></p>\n</div>",
