<td>No authentication</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Origin</td>\n            <td>Kashmir, India</td>\n            <td>Unknown source</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h4>Required Documentation</h4>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>GI Registry certification number</li>\n    <li>ISO 3632 compliance certificate</li>\n    <li>Laboratory test reports</li>\n    <li>Spices Board of India authentication</li>\n    <li>Farmer source traceability documents</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Storage &amp; Usage</h2>\n\n<h4>Proper Storage Guidelines</h4>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>Store in airtight container away from light</li>\n    <li>Keep in cool, dry place (below 20°C)</li>\n    <li>Avoid direct sunlight and moisture</li>\n    <li>Shelf life: 2-3 years when stored properly</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Usage Instructions</h4>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>Soak 8-10 threads in warm milk/water for 15-20 minutes</li>\n    <li>Use the liquid along with threads for maximum flavor</li>\n    <li>Add to dishes during final cooking stages</li>\n    <li>Recommended usage: 3-8 threads per serving</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Purchase Information</h2>\n\n<p>When you buy original saffron online from Kashmir Online Store, you invest in genuine Kashmiri heritage backed by proper certifications and laboratory reports. Our wholesale saffron supplier network ensures competitive pricing while maintaining premium quality standards.</p>\n\n<h4>Shipping Information</h4>\n\n<div class=\"highlight-box\">\n    <table>\n        <thead>\n            <tr>\n                <th>Shipping Zone</th>\n                <th>Delivery Time</th>\n                <th>Shipping Cost</th>\n                <th>Free Shipping Threshold</th>\n            </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Jammu &amp; Kashmir</td>\n                <td>1-2 days</td>\n                <td>₹50</td>\n                <td>Orders above ₹1000</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>North India (Delhi, Punjab, Haryana)</t