      "body_html": "<body>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #333;\n          \n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fefefe;\n        }\n        \n        h1 {\n            color: #8B4513;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid #8B4513;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        \n        h2 {\n            color: #DC143C;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border-left: 5px solid #DC143C;\n            padding-left: 15px;\n        }\n        \n        h3 {\n            color: #B22222;\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-top: 25px;\n            margin-bottom: 12px;\n        }\n        \n        h4 {\n            color: #8B0000;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        \n        table {\n            width: 100%;\n            border-collapse: collapse;\n            margin: 20px 0;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        \n        th, td {\n            padding: 12px;\n            text-align: left;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n        }\n        \n        th {\n            background-color: #DC143C;\n            color: white;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        \n        tr:nth-child(even) {\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n        }\n        \n        tr:hover {\n            background-color: #f5f5f5;\n        }\n        \n        ul {\n            margin: 15px 0;\n            padding-left: 25px;\n        }\n        \n        li {\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n        \n        .intro-text {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: #555;\n            background-color: #fff8dc;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-left: 4px solid #8B4513;\n        }\n        \n        .highlight-box {\n            background-color: #fff0f0;\n            border: 2px solid #DC143C;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin: 20px 0;\n        }\n        \n        .feature-list {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 15px;\n            margin: 20px 0;\n        }\n        \n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border-left: 3px solid #8B4513;\n        }\n        \n        .kesar-highlight {\n            color: #8B4513;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        \n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            body {\n                padding: 10px;\n            }\n            \n            h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            \n            h2 {\n                font-size: 1.5em;\n            }\n            \n            table {\n                font-size: 0.9em;\n            }\n            \n            th, td {\n                padding: 8px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"intro-text\">\n    Experience the authentic taste and aroma of pure <span class=\"kesar-highlight\">kesar</span> with our premium GI tagged Kashmiri saffron, sourced directly from the pristine saffron fields of Pampore by Kashmir Online Store. This handpicked Mongra saffron represents the finest quality Indian red gold, certified by the Geographical Indication Registry of India and meeting the highest standards of purity and authenticity.\n</div>\n\n<h2>Product Quality Standards</h2>\n\n<p>Our authentic saffron boasts exceptional crocin content and follows ISO 3632 certification standards, ensuring you receive only the finest grade A saffron threads. Each deep red stigma is carefully handpicked from the Crocus sativus flowers during the traditional harvesting season in Kashmir's high-altitude regions of Pulwama and Kishtwar.</p>\n\n<h3>Technical Specifications</h3>\n\n<table>\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th>Parameter</th>\n            <th>Our Kashmiri Saffron</th>\n            <th>ISO 3632 Standard</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Crocin Content</td>\n            <td>230-250</td>\n            <td>Min. 200</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Picrocrocin</td>\n            <td>70-90</td>\n            <td>Min. 70</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Safranal</td>\n            <td>35-50</td>\n            <td>Min. 30</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Moisture Content</td>\n            <td>&lt;12%</td>\n            <td>Max. 12%</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Thread Length</td>\n            <td>15-25mm</td>\n            <td>Premium Grade</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Color Grade</td>\n            <td>Grade I Mongra</td>\n            <td>Highest Quality</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>This organic saffron undergoes rigorous laboratory testing to guarantee zero adulteration and chemical-free purity. The long saffron threads deliver an intense, aroma-rich experience that distinguishes authentic Kashmiri saffron from inferior alternatives.</p>\n\n<h2>Traditional Heritage &amp; Certifications</h2>\n\n<p>Sourced from generations of traditional farmers in Kashmir saffron fields, our premium saffron maintains the time-honored manual harvesting methods while meeting contemporary quality certifications. The Spices Board of India recognition and Government of Jammu &amp; Kashmir authentication ensure complete traceability from farm to your kitchen.</p>\n\n<h4>Certification Details</h4>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>GI Registry India certification</li>\n    <li>ISO 3632 international compliance</li>\n    <li>Spices Board of India approval</li>\n    <li>Government of J&amp;K authentication</li>\n    <li>Laboratory purity verification</li>\n    <li>Zero adulteration guarantee</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Product Applications</h2>\n\n<p>Perfect for culinary enthusiasts and health-conscious consumers, this pure saffron enhances traditional cooking and has been valued in Ayurvedic practices for centuries. Known as zafran in traditional medicine, this premium saffron adds distinctive flavor, aroma, and natural properties to various preparations.</p>\n\n<h4>Culinary Uses</h4>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>Desserts &amp; Sweets: Kheer, kulfi, halwa, traditional mithai</li>\n    <li>Beverages: Golden milk, saffron tea, lassi, festive drinks</li>\n    <li>Rice Dishes: Biryani, pulao, aromatic rice preparations</li>\n    <li>Dairy Products: Flavored milk, yogurt, cheese preparations</li>\n    <li>Baking: Cakes, cookies, premium confectionery</li>\n    <li>Religious Offerings: Prasad preparation, temple ceremonies</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Traditional Applications</h4>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>Ayurvedic preparations and wellness recipes</li>\n    <li>Beauty and skincare traditional formulations</li>\n    <li>Ceremonial and religious practices</li>\n    <li>Premium gift items for special occasions</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Product Features</h2>\n\n<h4>Quality Assurance</h4>\n\n<div class=\"feature-list\">\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Authentic GI Certification: Verified by GI Registry India</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Premium Mongra Grade: Highest quality Lacha saffron</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Laboratory Tested: Complete purity verification with reports</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">ISO 3632 Compliant: International quality standards</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Zero Adulteration: Chemical-free and naturally pure</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Export Quality: Meeting international standards</div>\n</div>\n\n<h4>Source &amp; Supply</h4>\n\n<div class=\"feature-list\">\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Direct from Farmers: Fair trade practices, ensuring freshness</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Pampore Origin: Authentic Kashmir saffron fields</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Traditional Harvesting: Manual picking by experienced farmers</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Cold Storage: Proper preservation maintaining potency</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Complete Traceability: Farm-to-table documentation</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Quality Packaging: Airtight containers preserving freshness</div>\n</div>\n\n<h4>Kashmir Online Store Service</h4>\n\n<div class=\"feature-list\">\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Secure Online Delivery: Trusted sellers, nationwide shipping</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Wholesale Options: Bulk quantities for businesses</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Competitive Pricing: Best value for authentic GI saffron</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Expert Support: Usage and storage guidance</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Quality Guarantee: Satisfaction assured with authenticity</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">Fast Shipping: Quick delivery with proper packaging</div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Pricing &amp; Packages</h2>\n\n<h4>Available Options</h4>\n\n<table>\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th>Package Type</th>\n            <th>Weight</th>\n            <th>Ideal For</th>\n            <th>Features</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Starter Pack</td>\n            <td>2 grams</td>\n            <td>Regular home cooking</td>\n            <td>Perfect for beginners</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Family Pack</td>\n            <td>5 grams</td>\n            <td>Family occasions &amp; festivals</td>\n            <td>Most popular choice</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Premium Pack</td>\n            <td>10 grams</td>\n            <td>Frequent users &amp; small businesses</td>\n            <td>Better value per gram</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Bulk Pack</td>\n            <td>20 grams</td>\n            <td>Restaurants &amp; wholesale buyers</td>\n            <td>Maximum savings</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Authenticity Guide</h2>\n\n<h4>How to Identify Real Saffron</h4>\n\n<div class=\"highlight-box\">\n    <p><strong>Quick Tests:</strong></p>\n    <ol>\n        <li>\n<strong>Water Test:</strong> Real saffron slowly releases golden-yellow color</li>\n        <li>\n<strong>Aroma Test:</strong> Authentic saffron has sweet, hay-like fragrance</li>\n        <li>\n<strong>Thread Shape:</strong> Genuine threads have trumpet-shaped ends</li>\n        <li>\n<strong>Touch Test:</strong> Real saffron feels slightly oily, not completely dry</li>\n    </ol>\n</div>\n\n<h4>Authenticity Comparison</h4>\n\n<table>\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th>Feature</th>\n            <th>Our GI Saffron</th>\n            <th>Fake/Adulterated</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Color</td>\n            <td>Deep red threads</td>\n            <td>Artificially colored</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Aroma</td>\n            <td>Strong, distinctive</td>\n            <td>Weak/artificial</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Water Test</td>\n            <td>Golden yellow</td>\n            <td>Red/orange color</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Thread Structure</td>\n            <td>Trumpet-shaped ends</td>\n            <td>Cut/artificial</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Price</td>\n            <td>Premium but fair</td>\n            <td>Suspiciously cheap</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Certification</td>\n            <td>GI tag + Lab reports</td>\n            <td>No authentication</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>Origin</td>\n            <td>Kashmir, India</td>\n            <td>Unknown source</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h4>Required Documentation</h4>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>GI Registry certification number</li>\n    <li>ISO 3632 compliance certificate</li>\n    <li>Laboratory test reports</li>\n    <li>Spices Board of India authentication</li>\n    <li>Farmer source traceability documents</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Storage &amp; Usage</h2>\n\n<h4>Proper Storage Guidelines</h4>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>Store in airtight container away from light</li>\n    <li>Keep in cool, dry place (below 20°C)</li>\n    <li>Avoid direct sunlight and moisture</li>\n    <li>Shelf life: 2-3 years when stored properly</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Usage Instructions</h4>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>Soak 8-10 threads in warm milk/water for 15-20 minutes</li>\n    <li>Use the liquid along with threads for maximum flavor</li>\n    <li>Add to dishes during final cooking stages</li>\n    <li>Recommended usage: 3-8 threads per serving</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Purchase Information</h2>\n\n<p>When you buy original saffron online from Kashmir Online Store, you invest in genuine Kashmiri heritage backed by proper certifications and laboratory reports. Our wholesale saffron supplier network ensures competitive pricing while maintaining premium quality standards.</p>\n\n<h4>Shipping Information</h4>\n\n<div class=\"highlight-box\">\n    <table>\n        <thead>\n            <tr>\n                <th>Shipping Zone</th>\n                <th>Delivery Time</th>\n                <th>Shipping Cost</th>\n                <th>Free Shipping Threshold</th>\n            </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Jammu &amp; Kashmir</td>\n                <td>1-2 days</td>\n                <td>₹50</td>\n                <td>Orders above ₹1000</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>North India (Delhi, Punjab, Haryana)</td>\n                <td>2-3 days</td>\n                <td>₹80</td>\n                <td>Orders above ₹1500</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Rest of India</td>\n                <td>3-5 days</td>\n                <td>₹120</td>\n                <td>Orders above ₹2000</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Metro Cities (Express)</td>\n                <td>1-2 days</td>\n                <td>₹150</td>\n                <td>Orders above ₹2500</td>\n            </tr>\n        </tbody>\n    </table>\n</div>\n\n<h4>Wholesale Program</h4>\n\n<div class=\"feature-list\">\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">\n<strong>Minimum Order:</strong> 50 grams for wholesale pricing</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">\n<strong>Bulk Discounts:</strong> 15-25% off retail prices</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">\n<strong>Business Registration:</strong> Required for wholesale accounts</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">\n<strong>Payment Terms:</strong> Advance payment or 30-day credit for verified businesses</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">\n<strong>Custom Packaging:</strong> Private labeling available for 100g+ orders</div>\n    <div class=\"feature-item\">\n<strong>Dedicated Support:</strong> Direct contact with wholesale team</div>\n</div>\n\n<table>\n    <thead>\n        <tr>\n            <th>Wholesale Quantity</th>\n            <th>Discount Rate</th>\n            <th>Ideal For</th>\n            <th>Additional Benefits</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td>50-100 grams</td>\n            <td>15% off retail</td>\n            <td>Small retailers, cafes</td>\n            <td>Free shipping</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>100-250 grams</td>\n            <td>20% off retail</td>\n            <td>Restaurants, hotels</td>\n            <td>Custom packaging options</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>250-500 grams</td>\n            <td>22% off retail</td>\n            <td>Distributors, large restaurants</td>\n            <td>Priority shipping &amp; support</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td>500+ grams</td>\n            <td>25% off retail</td>\n            <td>Exporters, major distributors</td>\n            <td>Custom terms &amp; private labeling</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h4>Shipping &amp; Quality Guarantee</h4>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>\n<strong>Secure Packaging:</strong> Airtight containers with tamper-proof sealing</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Temperature Control:</strong> Insulated packaging for long-distance shipments</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Insurance Coverage:</strong> All shipments insured against damage or loss</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Tracking:</strong> Real-time order tracking via SMS and email</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Quality Assurance:</strong> 100% refund if product doesn't meet standards</li>\n    <li>\n<strong>Authenticity Guarantee:</strong> Certificate of authenticity with every order</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Understanding common concerns about fake saffron versus real saffron, we provide complete transparency through GI seals, test certificates, and detailed information about our cold-climate farming processes. The shelf life of our properly stored saffron extends significantly due to superior harvesting and processing methods.</p>\n\n<p>Transform your culinary experiences and embrace the rich tradition of authentic <span class=\"kesar-highlight\">kesar</span> - order your premium GI tagged Kashmiri saffron today from Kashmir Online Store and discover why discerning customers choose our certified, government-approved Indian saffron over ordinary alternatives.</p>\n\n\n</body>",
