y centuries-old Ayurvedic beauty traditions from Kashmir. Expertly formulated with a potent blend of skin-brightening, nourishing, and hydrating botanical actives, this glow serum works at the cellular level to revive your skin's natural luminosity.</p>\n<p>Whether you struggle with <em>dull skin</em>, <em>pigmentation</em>, <em>dark spots</em>, <em>dry skin</em>, or <em>uneven skin tone</em> — the Kumkumathi Radiance Serum is your daily ritual for glass-skin radiance. Lightweight, fast-absorbing, and suitable for all skin types, it blends seamlessly into your morning or night skincare routine.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Brightens dull and uneven skin tone within 2 weeks</li>\n<li>Deeply hydrates and repairs skin moisture barrier</li>\n<li>Reduces appearance of dark spots and pigmentation</li>\n<li>Restores natural skin glow and youthful radiance</li>\n<li>Improves skin texture, smoothness, and elasticity</li>\n<li>Lightweight serum — absorbs instantly, no greasy residue</li>\n<li>Safe for all skin types including sensitive skin</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<h3 style=\"font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size: 22px; color: var(--espresso); margin-bottom: 24px; font-weight: 600;\">Product Attributes</h3>\n<div class=\"attributes-grid\">\n<div class=\"attr-card\">\n<div class=\"attr-label\">Product Type</div>\n<div class=\"attr-value\">Brightening Face Serum</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"attr-card\">\n<div class=\"attr-label\">Volume</div>\n<div class=\"attr-value\">30 ml</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"attr-card\">\n<div class=\"attr-label\">Skin Type</div>\n<div class=\"attr-value\">All Skin Types</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"attr-card\">\n<div class=\"attr-label\">Key Concern</div>\n<div class=\"attr-value\">Dullness, Pigmentation, Dryness</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"attr-card\">\n<div class=\"attr-label\">Formula</div>\n<div class=\"attr-value\">Herbal · Ayurvedic · Natural</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"attr-card\">\n<div class=\"attr-label\">Usage</div>\n<div class=\"attr-value\">Morning &amp; Night</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"attr-card\">\n<div class=\"attr-label\">Hero Ingredient</div>\n<div class=\"attr-value\">Kashmiri Saffron, Pampore</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"attr-card\">\n<div class=\"attr-label\">Brand</div>\n<div class=\"attr-value\">Kashmir Online Store</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- INGREDIENT BENEFITS -->\n<section class=\"section ingredients-section\">\n<div style=\"color: var(--saffron-light);\" class=\"section-eyebrow\">Ingredient Benefits</div>\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">What's Inside Every Drop</h2>\n<p class=\"section-lead\">Each ingredient in the Kumkumathi Radiance Serum is carefully sourced from nature to deliver visible, lasting results — without a single synthetic chemical.</p>\n<div class=\"ingredients-grid\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<span class=\"ingredient-icon\">🌸</span>\n<div class=\"ingredient-name\">Kashmiri Saffron</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-desc\">Harvested from Pampore's famous saffron fields. Brightens complexion, reduces melanin production, and delivers intense antioxidant protection for luminous skin.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<span class=\"ingredient-icon\">🌿</span>\n<div class=\"ingredient-name\">Kumkumadi Oil</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-desc\">The sacred Ayurvedic elixir blended with 16 rare herbs. Targets dark spots, uneven tone, and dullness while deeply nourishing and restoring skin vitality.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<span class=\"ingredient-icon\">🪵</span>\n<div class=\"ingredient-name\">Sandalwood Extract</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-desc\">Known for centuries in Ayurvedic skincare. Soothes inflammation, evens skin tone, controls excess sebum, and imparts a naturally radiant, matte-glow finish.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<span class=\"ingredient-icon\">🌹</span>\n<div class=\"ingredient-name\">Rose Infusion</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-desc\">Hydrates at the deepest layers of skin, tightens pores, and delivers a refreshing surge of moisture that keeps skin plump, soft, and dewy throughout the day.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<span class=\"ingredient-icon\">💛</span>\n<div class=\"ingredient-name\">Turmeric (Haldi)</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-desc\">Nature's most powerful anti-inflammatory brightener. Fades dark spots, repairs sun damage, and promotes a visibly even, glowing complexion with consistent use.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<span class=\"ingredient-icon\">🫚</span>\n<div class=\"ingredient-name\">Cold-Pressed Oils</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-desc\">A nourishing blend of cold-pressed botanical oils that replenish lipids, restore the skin barrier, and provide lasting hydration without clogging pores.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<span class=\"ingredient-icon\">🌱</span>\n<div class=\"ingredient-name\">Herbal Botanical Complex</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-desc\">A synergistic blend of Ayurvedic herbs that enhances cell renewal, boosts collagen production, and delivers anti-aging benefits for firmer, youthful-looking skin.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<span class=\"ingredient-icon\">💧</span>\n<div class=\"ingredient-name\">Natural Skin Nutrients</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-desc\">Vitamins A, C, and E-rich natural extracts protect against environmental stressors, fade pigmentation, and enhance the skin's natural healing and glow mechanisms.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- HOW TO USE -->\n<section class=\"section how-to-use\">\n<div class=\"section-eyebrow\">Application Guide</div>\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">How to Use</h2>\n<p class=\"section-lead\">Follow this simple 4-step ritual morning and night for best results. Consistent use for 2–4 weeks reveals noticeably brighter, smoother, and more radiant skin.</p>\n<div class=\"steps-row\">\n<div class=\"step-card\">\n<div class=\"step-num\">1</div>\n<div class=\"step-title\">Cleanse</div>\n<div class=\"step-desc\">Begin with freshly cleansed, slightly damp skin. Use a gentle face wash suited for your skin type and pat dry with a soft towel.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"step-card\">\n<div class=\"step-num\">2</div>\n<div class=\"step-title\">Apply Serum</div>\n<div class=\"step-desc\">Take 3–4 drops of the Kumkumathi Radiance Serum onto your fingertips. Gently press and pat onto face and neck. Do not rub.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"step-card\">\n<div class=\"step-num\">3</div>\n<div class=\"step-title\">Massage</div>\n<div class=\"step-desc\">Using upward circular strokes, massage the serum gently for 60 seconds to boost absorption and stimulate circulation for that natural glow.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"step-card\">\n<div class=\"step-num\">4</div>\n<div class=\"step-title\">Moisturise &amp; Protect</div>\n<div class=\"step-desc\">Follow with your favourite moisturiser. In the morning, finish with SPF 30+ sunscreen to protect your freshly brightened skin from UV damage.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin-top: 48px; max-width: 720px;\">\n<div class=\"video-placeholder\">\n<div class=\"play-btn\">▶</div>\n<div class=\"video-label\">Watch: How to Apply Kumkumathi Radiance Serum</div>\n<div style=\"font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); margin-top: 4px;\">2 min · Application Tutorial</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- BEFORE & AFTER -->\n<section class=\"section before-after section-alt\">\n<div class=\"section-eyebrow\">Visible Results</div>\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">Before &amp; After Results</h2>\n<p class=\"section-lead\">Real skin transformations achieved by our customers using the Kumkumathi Radiance Serum consistently. Individual results may vary.</p>\n<div class=\"ba-grid\">\n<div class=\"ba-card\">\n<div class=\"ba-visual\">\n<div class=\"ba-before\">\n<span class=\"ba-emoji\">😔</span><span class=\"ba-label\">Before</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ba-divider\"><br></div>\n<div class=\"ba-after\">\n<span class=\"ba-emoji\">✨</span><span class=\"ba-label\">After</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ba-content\">\n<div class=\"ba-concern\">Dull, Tired Skin</div>\n<div class=\"ba-result\">Visibly brighter, well-rested complexion with natural radiance and improved overall skin luminosity.</div>\n<span class=\"ba-timeline\">Visible in 2 Weeks</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ba-card\">\n<div class=\"ba-visual\">\n<div class=\"ba-before\">\n<span class=\"ba-emoji\">🌑</span><span class=\"ba-label\">Before</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ba-divider\"><br></div>\n<div class=\"ba-after\">\n<span class=\"ba-emoji\">🌟</span><span class=\"ba-label\">After</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ba-content\">\n<div class=\"ba-concern\">Dark Spots &amp; Pigmentation</div>\n<div class=\"ba-result\">Significantly reduced appearance of dark spots, post-acne marks, and uneven pigmentation across the face.</div>\n<span class=\"ba-timeline\">Visible in 4 Weeks</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ba-card\">\n<div class=\"ba-visual\">\n<div class=\"ba-before\">\n<span class=\"ba-emoji\">🌵</span><span class=\"ba-label\">Before</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ba-divider\"><br></div>\n<div class=\"ba-after\">\n<span class=\"ba-emoji\">💧</span><span class=\"ba-label\">After</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ba-content\">\n<div class=\"ba-concern\">Dry, Dehydrated Skin</div>\n<div class=\"ba-result\">Deeply hydrated, plump, and supple skin with a healthy dewy glow and noticeably improved skin texture.</div>\n<span class=\"ba-timeline\">Visible in 1 Week</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- REVIEWS -->\n<section class=\"section reviews-section\">\n<div style=\"color: var(--saffron-light);\" class=\"section-eyebrow\">Customer Reviews</div>\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">What Our Customers Say</h2>\n<p style=\"color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);\" class=\"section-lead\">Rated 4.9/5 by 238 verified buyers. Loved across India for visible brightening and glow results.</p>\n<div class=\"reviews-grid\">\n<div class=\"review-card\">\n<div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n<div class=\"review-text\">\"I've tried so many brightening serums but the Kumkumathi Radiance Serum is something else. In just 10 days my skin started glowing and my dark spots have visibly faded. The saffron really works!\"</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-name\">Ayesha Malik</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-meta\">Mumbai, Maharashtra · 3 weeks ago</div>\n<div class=\"review-verified\">✔ Verified Purchase</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review-card\">\n<div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n<div class=\"review-text\">\"Perfect serum for dry skin! My skin feels so hydrated and soft from the very first application. The texture is silky and it absorbs so fast. Will definitely repurchase!\"</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-name\">Priya Sharma</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-meta\">Delhi, NCR · 1 month ago</div>\n<div class=\"review-verified\">✔ Verified Purchase</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review-card\">\n<div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n<div class=\"review-text\">\"The scent of saffron and roses is absolutely divine. My skin looks like I've been to a spa every day. Best herbal serum I've used — natural, effective, and so luxurious!\"</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-name\">Farah Qureshi</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-meta\">Hyderabad, Telangana · 2 months ago</div>\n<div class=\"review-verified\">✔ Verified Purchase</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review-card\">\n<div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★☆</div>\n<div class=\"review-text\">\"I ordered this as a bridal glow skincare prep and I'm so glad I did! Started 4 weeks before the wedding and the difference in my complexion is stunning. Everyone noticed.\"</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-name\">Neha Kapoor</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-meta\">Pune, Maharashtra · 3 months ago</div>\n<div class=\"review-verified\">✔ Verified Purchase</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review-card\">\n<div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n<div class=\"review-text\">\"Tried this for my pigmentation and uneven skin tone issues. After 3 weeks there's a clear brightening effect. Highly recommend to anyone looking for natural skincare in India.\"</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-name\">Deepika Iyer</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-meta\">Bengaluru, Karnataka · 1 month ago</div>\n<div class=\"review-verified\">✔ Verified Purchase</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review-card\">\n<div class=\"review-stars\">★★★★★</div>\n<div class=\"review-text\">\"The Kashmiri saffron serum has transformed my night skincare routine. Wake up every morning to soft, plump, glowing skin. Absolutely love this product from Kashmir Online Store!\"</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-name\">Sana Mir</div>\n<div class=\"reviewer-meta\">Srinagar, J&amp;K · 2 weeks ago</div>\n<div class=\"review-verified\">✔ Verified Purchase</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- FAQs -->\n<section class=\"section faq-section\">\n<div class=\"section-eyebrow\">Frequently Asked Questions</div>\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">Got Questions? We've Got Answers.</h2>\n<div style=\"margin-top: 40px;\" class=\"faq-list\">\n<details>\n<summary class=\"faq-question\">Is the Kumkumathi Radiance Serum suitable for sensitive skin? <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span></summary>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes, the Kumkumathi Radiance Serum is formulated with 100% natural, plant-based ingredients and is free from synthetic chemicals, parabens, sulphates, and artificial fragrances. It is gentle enough for sensitive skin. However, we always recommend doing a patch test before full application if you have highly reactive skin.</div>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary class=\"faq-question\">How soon will I see results? <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span></summary>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Most customers notice improved hydration and a subtle glow within the first 5–7 days. Visible brightening and reduction in dullness typically appear within 2 weeks of consistent daily use. For dark spots and pigmentation correction, we recommend continued use for 4–6 weeks for optimal results.</div>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary class=\"faq-question\">Can I use this serum in the morning and at night? <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span></summary>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Absolutely. The Kumkumathi Radiance Serum is designed for both morning and night use. In the morning, follow with a broad-spectrum SPF moisturiser to protect your skin. At night, it works as an intensive repair and brightening serum while your skin renews itself.</div>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary class=\"faq-question\">Is this serum Ayurvedic? Does it contain chemicals? <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span></summary>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">The Kumkumathi Radiance Serum is inspired by Ayurvedic herbal traditions and is crafted exclusively with natural botanical ingredients. It contains zero synthetic chemicals, preservatives, parabens, sulphates, or artificial colourants. What you get is pure herbal skincare in every drop.</div>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary class=\"faq-question\">What is the shelf life of the serum? <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span></summary>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">The Kumkumathi Radiance Serum has a shelf life of 18 months from the date of manufacture when stored correctly. Keep the bottle in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. After opening, use within 6 months for best potency and freshness.</div>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary class=\"faq-question\">Do you offer Cash on Delivery (COD)? <span class=\"faq-icon\">+</span></summary>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes! We offer Cash on Delivery (COD) across India. You can place your order with full confidence and pay only when your product is delivered to your doorstep. We also support all major UPI apps, credit/debit cards, and net banking for prepaid orders.</div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</section>\n<!-- PRODUCT SPECS -->\n<section class=\"section specs-section\">\n<div class=\"section-eyebrow\">Specifications</div>\n<h2 class=\"section-title\">Product Details</h2>\n<p class=\"section-lead\">Complete product specifications for the Kumkumathi Radiance Serum.</p>\n<table class=\"specs-table\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Product Name</td>\n<td>Kumkumathi Radiance Serum</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Brand</td>\n<td>Kashmir Online Store</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Volume / Size</td>\n<td>30 ml</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Product Category</td>\n<td>Brightening Face Serum · Herbal Serum · Glow Serum</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Skin Type</td>\n<td>All Skin Types (Normal, Dry, Oily, Combination, Sensitive)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Key Skin Concerns</td>\n<td>Dullness · Pigmentation · Dark Spots · Dehydration · Uneven Skin Tone</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Primary Ingredients</td>\n<td>Kashmiri Saffron Extract · Kumkumadi Oil · Sandalwood Extract · Rose Infusion · Turmeric · Herbal Botanical Complex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Formula Type</td>\n<td>100% Natural · Herbal · Ayurvedic-Inspired · Plant-Based</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Free From</td>\n<td>Parabens · Sulphates · Synthetic Chemicals · Artificial Fragrance · Mineral Oil</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Country of Origin</td>\n<td>India</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Usage</td>\n<td>Morning &amp; Night Routine · Daily Use</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Recommended Use</td>\n<td>Apply 3–4 drops on cleansed face and neck, massage gently until absorbed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Shelf Life</td>\n<td>18 months (6 months after opening)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Packaging</td>\n<td>Dropper Bottle · Recyclable Glass</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"certs-row\">\n<div class=\"cert-badge\">\n<span class=\"icon\">🌿</span> 100% Natural Ingredients</div>\n<div class=\"cert-badge\">\n<span class=\"icon\">🐰</span> Cruelty-Free</div>\n<div class=\"cert-badge\">\n<span class=\"icon\">🧪</span> Dermatologically Tested</div>\n<div class=\"cert-badge\">\n<span class=\"icon\">🇮🇳</span> Made in India</div>\n<div class=\"cert-badge\">\n<span class=\"icon\">♻️</span> Eco-Friendly Packaging</div>\n<div class=\"cert-badge\">\n<span class=\"icon\">✅</span> No Parabens · No Sulphates</div>\n</div>\n