      "body_html": "<p><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"> <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Original Kumkumathi Radiance Oil by Kashmir Online Store. A luxurious Ayurvedic facial oil with Kashmiri Saffron from Pampore, Kumkumathi Oil Blend, Botanical Carrier Oils and Vitamin E. Brightens, nourishes and revitalizes skin. 30 ml.\"> <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,600&amp;family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"></p>\n<style>\n  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n\n  body {\n    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;\n    background: #faf6ee;\n    color: #1c1c1c;\n    line-height: 1.75;\n    padding: 48px 24px;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  /* ── BRAND ── */\n  .brand-label {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 3px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #b8902a;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── TITLE ── */\n  .product-eyebrow {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-style: italic;\n    color: #9a7a3a;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  h1 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 52px);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1e0f00;\n    line-height: 1.12;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n  }\n  .product-descriptor {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    font-style: italic;\n    color: #7a5c1e;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    letter-spacing: 0.3px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── PILLAR TAGS ── */\n  .pillars {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 8px;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n  .pillar {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #1e0f00;\n    background: transparent;\n    border: 1.5px solid #c9a84c;\n    padding: 5px 16px;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── ORIGIN + NET QTY ROW ── */\n  .meta-row {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 10px;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    margin-bottom: 32px;\n  }\n  .meta-tag {\n    display: inline-flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 7px;\n    background: #fff4e0;\n    border: 1px solid #e8c97a;\n    color: #7a4f00;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    padding: 6px 16px;\n    border-radius: 3px;\n  }\n  .meta-tag.dark {\n    background: #1e0f00;\n    border-color: #1e0f00;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n  }\n\n  /* ── INTRO ── */\n  .intro {\n    font-size: 15.5px;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n    line-height: 1.95;\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\n    padding-left: 18px;\n    border-left: 3px solid #c9a84c;\n    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;\n  }\n\n  /* ── SECTION HEADINGS ── */\n  h2 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 26px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1e0f00;\n    margin: 44px 0 16px;\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n  }\n\n  /* ── SAFFRON HERO BLOCK ── */\n  .saffron-hero {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e0f00 0%, #2e1800 60%, #3d2208 100%);\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    padding: 36px 32px;\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  .saffron-hero::before {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    top: -60px; right: -60px;\n    width: 220px; height: 220px;\n    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n  }\n  .saffron-hero::after {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: -40px; left: -40px;\n    width: 160px; height: 160px;\n    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n  }\n  .saffron-hero-label {\n    font-size: 10px;\n    letter-spacing: 3px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.7);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    position: relative;\n    z-index: 2;\n  }\n  .saffron-hero h3 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 30px);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    line-height: 1.25;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n    position: relative;\n    z-index: 2;\n  }\n  .saffron-hero p {\n    font-size: 14.5px;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);\n    line-height: 1.9;\n    position: relative;\n    z-index: 2;\n    max-width: 620px;\n  }\n  .saffron-facts {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 0;\n    margin-top: 28px;\n    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);\n    padding-top: 22px;\n    position: relative;\n    z-index: 2;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n  }\n  .saffron-fact {\n    flex: 1;\n    min-width: 140px;\n    padding-right: 24px;\n  }\n  .saffron-fact:not(:last-child) {\n    border-right: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);\n    margin-right: 24px;\n  }\n  .saffron-fact-label {\n    font-size: 10px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.6);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 5px;\n  }\n  .saffron-fact-value {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    font-weight: 500;\n  }\n\n  /* ── BENEFITS ── */\n  .benefits-list { list-style: none; }\n  .benefits-list li {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 18px;\n    padding: 18px 0;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #ede6d4;\n    font-size: 14.5px;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n  }\n  .benefits-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n  .benefit-icon {\n    width: 40px; height: 40px;\n    background: #fff4e0;\n    border: 1px solid #e8c97a;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    margin-top: 1px;\n  }\n  .benefit-text b {\n    display: block;\n    color: #1e0f00;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 3px;\n    letter-spacing: 0.2px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── INGREDIENTS ── */\n  .ingredient-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    padding: 0;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n  }\n  .ingredient-header {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 16px;\n    padding: 20px 24px;\n    background: #1e0f00;\n  }\n  .ingredient-num {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 36px;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.5);\n    line-height: 1;\n    min-width: 36px;\n  }\n  .ingredient-title-wrap h3 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    margin-bottom: 3px;\n  }\n  .ingredient-title-wrap span {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 1.5px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);\n    font-weight: 500;\n  }\n  .ingredient-body {\n    padding: 18px 24px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #4a4a4a;\n    line-height: 1.8;\n  }\n  .ingredient-body b { color: #1e0f00; }\n\n  /* Star ingredient */\n  .ingredient-card.star .ingredient-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e0f00, #3d2208); }\n  .ingredient-card.star .ingredient-header::after {\n    content: '★ Hero Ingredient';\n    font-size: 10px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.8);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    margin-left: auto;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  }\n\n  /* ── DIRECTIONS ── */\n  .directions-block {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    padding: 6px 26px 6px;\n  }\n  .directions-block ol { list-style: none; counter-reset: d; }\n  .directions-block ol li {\n    counter-increment: d;\n    padding: 15px 0 15px 48px;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0e8d5;\n    font-size: 14.5px;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .directions-block ol li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n  .directions-block ol li::before {\n    content: counter(d);\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 0; top: 13px;\n    width: 30px; height: 30px;\n    background: #1e0f00;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    line-height: 30px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n  }\n  .pro-tip {\n    margin-top: 18px;\n    padding: 15px 20px;\n    background: #fff4e0;\n    border-left: 3px solid #c9a84c;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #2c1a0e;\n    line-height: 1.75;\n  }\n\n  /* ── RITUAL GUIDE ── */\n  .ritual-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 12px;\n  }\n  .ritual-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-top: 3px solid #c9a84c;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 22px 18px 20px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .ritual-icon { font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; }\n  .ritual-card h4 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 17px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1e0f00;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  .ritual-card p { font-size: 13px; color: #5a5a5a; line-height: 1.65; }\n\n  /* ── SUITABLE FOR ── */\n  .suitable-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .suitable-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 18px 14px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #4a4a4a;\n    line-height: 1.55;\n  }\n  .suitable-card .s-icon { font-size: 24px; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }\n  .suitable-card b { display: block; color: #1e0f00; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }\n\n  /* ── CAUTION ── */\n  .caution-block {\n    margin-top: 44px;\n    padding: 16px 20px;\n    background: #fff9f0;\n    border: 1px solid #f0d8a0;\n    border-left: 4px solid #d4a017;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 13.5px;\n    color: #5a3e00;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n  }\n  .caution-block b { color: #3a2800; }\n\n  @media (max-width: 600px) {\n    .ritual-grid, .suitable-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n    .saffron-facts { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }\n    .saffron-fact:not(:last-child) { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); padding-bottom: 16px; margin-right: 0; }\n  }\n</style>\n<!-- ── TITLE BLOCK ── -->\n<p class=\"brand-label\">Kashmir Online Store · Skincare</p>\n<p class=\"product-eyebrow\">Traditional Ayurvedic Beauty Oil</p>\n<h1>Original Kumkumathi<br>Radiance Oil</h1>\n<p class=\"product-descriptor\">Brightens  •  Nourishes  •  Revitalizes</p>\n<div class=\"pillars\">\n<span class=\"pillar\">Brightening</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Nourishing</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Revitalizing</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Ayurvedic</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"meta-row\">\n<span class=\"meta-tag\">🌸 Kashmiri Saffron — Pampore, Kashmir</span> <span class=\"meta-tag dark\">Net Qty: 30 ml</span>\n</div>\n<!-- ── INTRO ── -->\n<p class=\"intro\">The <strong>Original Kumkumathi Radiance Oil</strong> is a luxurious Ayurvedic facial oil crafted with precious <strong>Kumkumathi herbs</strong>, <strong>pure Kashmiri Saffron</strong> from the saffron fields of <strong>Pampore, Kashmir</strong>, nourishing <strong>botanical carrier oils</strong>, and skin-protecting <strong>Vitamin E</strong>. This time-honoured traditional formulation works deeply to improve skin radiance, restore your natural glow, and support a visibly smoother, softer, and healthier complexion. Not a shortcut — a ritual. The kind passed down through generations and now brought to you in its most authentic form.</p>\n<!-- ── SAFFRON HERO ── -->\n<div class=\"saffron-hero\">\n<p class=\"saffron-hero-label\">★ The Heart of This Formula</p>\n<h3>Kashmiri Saffron from Pampore —<br>The World's Most Precious Skincare Ingredient</h3>\n<p>At the core of the Kumkumathi Radiance Oil is <strong>pure Kashmiri Saffron</strong> — sourced directly from the ancient saffron fields of <strong>Pampore</strong>, the saffron capital of India. Pampore's saffron is globally recognised for its unmatched depth of colour, intensity of aroma, and exceptional concentration of active compounds. In skincare, Kashmiri Saffron is revered for its ability to brighten the complexion, improve skin tone uniformity, reduce dullness, and impart a lasting luminosity that no synthetic alternative can replicate. Every drop of this oil carries the essence of Kashmir's most treasured botanical.</p>\n<div class=\"saffron-facts\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Origin</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">Pampore, Kashmir Valley</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Key Compound</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">Crocin &amp; Safranal</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Skin Action</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">Brightens · Evens Tone · Glows</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Grade</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">Pure · Hand-Harvested</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── BENEFITS ── -->\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\n<ul class=\"benefits-list\">\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">✨</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Enhances Natural Skin Radiance and Glow</b> Kashmiri Saffron's crocin compound works at the skin surface to brighten complexion, even out tone, and restore the kind of luminous, healthy glow that dullness and fatigue take away. With daily use, skin looks visibly more alive and radiant.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🌗</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Helps Reduce Dullness and Uneven Skin Tone</b> The Kumkumathi oil blend and saffron actives work together to gently address areas of uneven pigmentation, dark spots, and discolouration — bringing the complexion back into a more balanced, harmonious tone over time.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🌿</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Deeply Nourishes and Improves Skin Softness</b> Botanical carrier oils and Vitamin E penetrate deeply into the skin barrier, delivering sustained nourishment that leaves skin noticeably softer, smoother, and more supple — especially with nightly use.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🪷</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Supports Smoother and Healthier-Looking Skin</b> The traditional Ayurvedic formulation works in concert with the skin's natural overnight repair cycle — supporting cell renewal, improving texture, and restoring a visibly healthier and more youthful-looking complexion.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- ── KEY INGREDIENTS ── -->\n<h2>Key Ingredients</h2>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card star\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">01</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Kashmiri Saffron — Pampore, Kashmir</h3>\n<span>Pure · Hand-Harvested · Hero Ingredient</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">The single most important ingredient in this formulation. <b>Pure Kashmiri Saffron</b> sourced from Pampore — the saffron heartland of India — is packed with <b>crocin, crocetin, and safranal</b>. These rare compounds brighten the complexion, reduce melanin overproduction responsible for dark spots and uneven tone, and deliver a warm, natural radiance that builds with consistent use. Kashmiri Saffron has been a cornerstone of traditional Indian beauty rituals for thousands of years — and for good reason. Nothing else brightens the skin the way it does.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">02</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Kumkumathi Oil Blend</h3>\n<span>Traditional Ayurvedic Herbal Complex</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">The ancient Kumkumathi formulation is an Ayurvedic heritage blend — a precise combination of herbs, resins, and botanicals traditionally used to nourish the skin, improve complexion, and restore natural radiance. It brings centuries of traditional beauty wisdom into each drop of this oil, forming the trusted backbone of this formulation.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">03</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Botanical Carrier Oils</h3>\n<span>Plant-Derived Nourishing Base</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">A carefully chosen blend of <b>plant-based carrier oils</b> that form the nourishing base of this facial oil. These oils are selected for their affinity with facial skin — lightweight enough to absorb well, rich enough to deliver deep and lasting moisture, and perfectly suited to carry the active herbal compounds deep into the skin layers where they are needed most.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">04</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Vitamin E</h3>\n<span>Antioxidant Skin Protector</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">\n<b>Pure Vitamin E (Tocopherol)</b> is a powerful fat-soluble antioxidant that protects the skin from oxidative stress and environmental damage. It supports the skin's natural healing process, improves moisture retention, and helps maintain the stability and freshness of the botanical oils in the formulation — making every drop as potent as the first.</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── DIRECTIONS ── -->\n<h2>Directions for Use</h2>\n<div class=\"directions-block\">\n<ol>\n<li>Begin with a clean, dry face and neck — free from makeup and impurities.</li>\n<li>Dispense 2–3 drops of Kumkumathi Radiance Oil onto your fingertips or palm.</li>\n<li>Gently warm the oil between your fingers for a few seconds to activate the botanical compounds.</li>\n<li>Apply to the face and neck, then massage in gentle upward circular motions until fully absorbed. Pay extra attention to areas of dullness or uneven tone.</li>\n<li>Allow the oil to absorb fully. Do not rinse. Follow with nothing — let the oil work undisturbed overnight.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pro-tip\">🌙 <strong>Best Results:</strong> Use nightly before bed. The skin's overnight repair cycle makes it the ideal time for botanical oils to work — absorption is deeper, and the active compounds in Kashmiri Saffron and Kumkumathi herbs have uninterrupted time to brighten, nourish, and restore.</div>\n<!-- ── RITUAL GUIDE ── -->\n<h2>How to Build Your Radiance Ritual</h2>\n<div class=\"ritual-grid\">\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">🧖</div>\n<h4>Step 1 — Cleanse</h4>\n<p>Start with a gentle, natural cleanser to remove the day's impurities and prepare the skin for full oil absorption.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">💧</div>\n<h4>Step 2 — Tone (Optional)</h4>\n<p>Apply a natural facial toner or rose water to balance skin pH and slightly dampen the skin — oil absorbs beautifully on lightly damp skin.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">🪷</div>\n<h4>Step 3 — Radiance Oil</h4>\n<p>Apply 2–3 drops of Kumkumathi Radiance Oil and massage in upward circular motions. Leave on overnight and let saffron and herbs work their magic.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── SUITABLE FOR ── -->\n<h2>Suitable For</h2>\n<div class=\"suitable-grid\">\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌗</span> <b>Dull Skin</b> Restores radiance and glow to tired, lacklustre skin</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌑</span> <b>Uneven Skin Tone</b> Gently addresses dark spots and pigmentation over time</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌵</span> <b>Dry &amp; Dehydrated Skin</b> Deeply nourishes and restores moisture-starved skin</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌙</span> <b>Night Skincare Ritual</b> Designed for nightly use — works with skin's repair cycle</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">👰</span> <b>Bridal Skincare</b> Begin 6–8 weeks before for a visible pre-bridal glow</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌿</span> <b>All Skin Types</b> Balanced botanical formula — suitable for normal, dry and combination skin</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── CAUTION ── -->\n<div class=\"caution-block\">⚠️ <b>Caution:</b> For external use only. Avoid direct contact with eyes. If contact occurs, rinse immediately with plenty of clean water. Perform a patch test before first use if you have sensitive skin. Discontinue use if any irritation occurs. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight.</div>",
