      "title": "Luxury Glow Facial Oil ( Premium Botanical Facial Oil )",
      "handle": "luxury-glow-facial-oil",
      "body_html": "<p><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"> <meta content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" name=\"viewport\"><meta content=\"Luxury Glow Facial Oil by Kashmir Online Store. A premium botanical facial oil with Kumkumathi Oil, Jojoba Oil, Rosehip Oil, Pomegranate Oil and Botanical Essential Oils. Deeply nourishes, restores radiance and supports a smoother, luminous complexion.\" name=\"description\"> <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,600&amp;family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&amp;display=swap\"></p>\n<style>\n  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n\n  body {\n    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;\n    background: #faf7f3;\n    color: #1c1c1c;\n    line-height: 1.75;\n    padding: 48px 24px;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  /* ── BRAND ── */\n  .brand-label {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 3px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #b8902a;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── TITLE ── */\n  .product-eyebrow {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-style: italic;\n    color: #9a7a3a;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  h1 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 54px);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1a1208;\n    line-height: 1.1;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n  }\n  .product-descriptor {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 17px;\n    font-style: italic;\n    color: #8a6820;\n    margin-bottom: 22px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── PILLARS ── */\n  .pillars {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 8px;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n  }\n  .pillar {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #1a1208;\n    border: 1.5px solid #c9a84c;\n    padding: 5px 16px;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── INTRO ── */\n  .intro {\n    font-size: 15.5px;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n    line-height: 1.95;\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\n    padding-left: 18px;\n    border-left: 3px solid #c9a84c;\n  }\n\n  /* ── SECTION HEADING ── */\n  h2 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 26px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1a1208;\n    margin: 44px 0 16px;\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n  }\n\n  /* ── BENEFITS ── */\n  .benefits-list { list-style: none; }\n  .benefits-list li {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 18px;\n    padding: 18px 0;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #ede6d4;\n    font-size: 14.5px;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n  }\n  .benefits-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n  .benefit-icon {\n    width: 40px; height: 40px;\n    background: #fff8ee;\n    border: 1px solid #e8c97a;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    margin-top: 2px;\n  }\n  .benefit-text b {\n    display: block;\n    color: #1a1208;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── INGREDIENTS ── */\n  .ingredient-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n  }\n  .ingredient-header {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 16px;\n    padding: 20px 24px;\n    background: #1a1208;\n  }\n  .ingredient-num {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 36px;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.45);\n    line-height: 1;\n    min-width: 36px;\n  }\n  .ingredient-title-wrap h3 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    margin-bottom: 3px;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n  }\n  .ingredient-title-wrap span {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 1.5px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);\n    font-weight: 500;\n  }\n  .ingredient-body {\n    padding: 20px 24px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #4a4a4a;\n    line-height: 1.82;\n  }\n  .ingredient-body b { color: #1a1208; }\n\n  /* skin-action tags inside ingredient body */\n  .action-tags {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 6px;\n    margin-top: 12px;\n  }\n  .action-tag {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #7a4f00;\n    background: #fff8ee;\n    border: 1px solid #e8c97a;\n    padding: 3px 10px;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── DIRECTIONS ── */\n  .directions-block {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    padding: 6px 26px 6px;\n  }\n  .directions-block ol { list-style: none; counter-reset: d; }\n  .directions-block ol li {\n    counter-increment: d;\n    padding: 15px 0 15px 50px;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0e8d5;\n    font-size: 14.5px;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .directions-block ol li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n  .directions-block ol li::before {\n    content: counter(d);\n    position: absolute; left: 0; top: 13px;\n    width: 30px; height: 30px;\n    background: #1a1208;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    line-height: 30px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n  }\n\n  .pro-tip {\n    margin-top: 18px;\n    padding: 15px 20px;\n    background: #fff8ee;\n    border-left: 3px solid #c9a84c;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #2c1a0e;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n  }\n\n  /* ── USE RITUAL ── */\n  .ritual-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 12px;\n  }\n  .ritual-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-top: 3px solid #c9a84c;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 22px 18px 20px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .ritual-icon { font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; }\n  .ritual-card h4 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 17px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1a1208;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  .ritual-card p { font-size: 13px; color: #5a5a5a; line-height: 1.65; }\n\n  /* ── SUITABLE FOR ── */\n  .suitable-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .suitable-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 18px 14px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #4a4a4a;\n    line-height: 1.55;\n  }\n  .suitable-card .s-icon { font-size: 24px; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }\n  .suitable-card b { display: block; color: #1a1208; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }\n\n  /* ── STORAGE + SHELF LIFE ── */\n  .storage-row {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 12px;\n    margin-top: 4px;\n  }\n  .storage-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 18px 20px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 14px;\n  }\n  .storage-icon { font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }\n  .storage-card h4 {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    letter-spacing: 1.5px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #9a9a9a;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 5px;\n  }\n  .storage-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #3a3a3a; line-height: 1.6; }\n\n  /* ── CAUTION ── */\n  .caution-block {\n    margin-top: 44px;\n    padding: 16px 20px;\n    background: #fff9f0;\n    border: 1px solid #f0d8a0;\n    border-left: 4px solid #d4a017;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 13.5px;\n    color: #5a3e00;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n  }\n  .caution-block b { color: #3a2800; }\n\n  @media (max-width: 600px) {\n    .ritual-grid, .suitable-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n    .storage-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"pillars\">\n<span class=\"pillar\">Glow</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Nourishing</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Revitalizing</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Botanical</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Lightweight</span>\n</div>\n<!-- ── INTRO ── -->\n<p class=\"intro\">The <strong>Luxury Glow Facial Oil</strong> is a premium botanical facial oil crafted with a curated blend of <strong>Kumkumathi Oil</strong>, <strong>Jojoba Oil</strong>, <strong>Rosehip Oil</strong>, <strong>Pomegranate Oil</strong>, and <strong>Botanical Essential Oils</strong> — chosen for their exceptional affinity with facial skin and their proven ability to nourish, repair, and illuminate. This <strong>lightweight yet deeply nourishing formula</strong> absorbs beautifully into the skin, delivering active botanical compounds exactly where the skin needs them most. The result — restored natural glow, improved softness, and a visibly smoother, more luminous complexion that feels as good as it looks.</p>\n<!-- ── BENEFITS ── -->\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\n<ul class=\"benefits-list\">\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🌿</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Deeply Nourishes and Revitalizes the Skin</b> The multi-oil botanical blend penetrates the skin's upper layers to deliver sustained, deep nourishment — replenishing depleted moisture reserves, reviving tired skin, and restoring the sense of vitality that environmental stress and daily wear strip away.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">✨</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Helps Restore Natural Radiance and Glow</b> Kumkumathi Oil and Rosehip work together to brighten the complexion from within — addressing dullness and uneven tone to reveal the natural, healthy radiance your skin already holds, brought back to the surface.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🪷</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Improves Skin Softness and Smooth Texture</b> Jojoba Oil and Pomegranate Oil are rich in fatty acids and antioxidants that soften rough texture, smooth the skin surface, and improve overall skin feel — noticeably silkier and more refined with consistent use.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🌸</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Supports Healthier and More Luminous Skin</b> The botanical essential oil blend works synergistically with the carrier oils to support the skin's natural renewal process — encouraging a clearer, brighter, and more luminous complexion over time.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">💧</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Leaves Skin Silky, Supple, and Refreshed</b> Unlike heavy facial oils that sit on the surface, this lightweight formula absorbs cleanly — leaving behind nothing but skin that feels genuinely silky, supple, and refreshed. No greasiness. No residue.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- ── KEY INGREDIENTS ── -->\n<h2>Key Ingredients</h2>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">01</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Kumkumathi Oil</h3>\n<span>Traditional Ayurvedic Brightening Oil</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">A revered Ayurvedic oil blend rooted in centuries of traditional Indian beauty practice. <b>Kumkumathi Oil</b> is formulated from a combination of precious herbs and botanical oils traditionally used to improve skin tone, restore radiance, and nourish the complexion. It brings heritage-backed brightening power to the heart of this formulation.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Brightening</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Tone Correcting</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Radiance Restoring</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">02</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Jojoba Oil</h3>\n<span>Skin-Identical Balancing Carrier Oil</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">Technically a liquid wax, <b>Jojoba Oil</b> is molecularly similar to the skin's own sebum — making it one of the most skin-compatible oils in existence. It absorbs effortlessly without clogging pores, balances oil production, and delivers exceptional moisture to the skin barrier. The foundation of this oil's lightweight, non-greasy feel.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Deep Moisturising</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Pore-Friendly</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Balancing</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">03</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Rosehip Oil</h3>\n<span>Vitamin A &amp; C Rich Regenerating Oil</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">Cold-pressed from rosehip seeds, <b>Rosehip Oil</b> is one of the most nutrient-dense botanical oils for facial skin. Naturally rich in <b>Vitamin A (retinol precursor)</b>, <b>Vitamin C</b>, and essential fatty acids, it accelerates skin cell renewal, visibly reduces dark spots and hyperpigmentation, and improves skin texture and firmness over consistent use.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Skin Renewal</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Dark Spot Reduction</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Firming</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Brightening</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">04</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Pomegranate Oil</h3>\n<span>Antioxidant-Rich Regenerating Oil</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">Extracted from pomegranate seeds, <b>Pomegranate Oil</b> is exceptionally rich in <b>Punicic acid</b> — a rare omega-5 fatty acid found almost exclusively in this oil. It delivers powerful antioxidant protection, supports collagen integrity, improves skin elasticity, and promotes a noticeably more plump, supple skin feel with regular use.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Antioxidant</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Elasticity</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Plumping</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Protective</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">05</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Botanical Essential Oils</h3>\n<span>Aromatic Active Botanical Blend</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">A carefully selected blend of <b>plant-derived aromatic essential oils</b> that bring both therapeutic skin benefits and a naturally beautiful sensory experience to each application. These oils work synergistically with the carrier oil base — enhancing absorption, supporting skin clarity, and contributing to the overall luminosity and health of the complexion.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Skin Clarity</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Aromatic</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Synergistic</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── DIRECTIONS ── -->\n<h2>Directions for Use</h2>\n<div class=\"directions-block\">\n<ol>\n<li>Begin with a thoroughly cleansed, dry face and neck.</li>\n<li>Dispense 2–3 drops of Luxury Glow Facial Oil onto your fingertips or palm.</li>\n<li>Gently warm the oil between your palms for a few seconds to awaken the botanical compounds.</li>\n<li>Apply to the face and neck, massaging in gentle upward circular motions until fully absorbed. Focus on areas of dryness, dullness, or uneven texture.</li>\n<li>Use alone as your final skincare step, or layer over your serum for enhanced nourishment and a deeper glow.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pro-tip\">💡 <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> For a luminous base before makeup, use just 1 drop mixed with your foundation or applied on bare skin — it creates a natural, lit-from-within glow finish. For deep overnight nourishment, apply 2–3 drops as the final step in your night ritual and let the botanical oils work while you sleep.</div>\n<!-- ── USE RITUAL ── -->\n<h2>Build Your Glow Ritual</h2>\n<div class=\"ritual-grid\">\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">🧖</div>\n<h4>Step 1 — Cleanse</h4>\n<p>Start with a natural cleanser to remove impurities and open the skin to full botanical absorption.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">💧</div>\n<h4>Step 2 — Serum (Optional)</h4>\n<p>Apply your serum first if using one. The facial oil layers beautifully over serum for a deeper nourishment effect.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">✨</div>\n<h4>Step 3 — Glow Oil</h4>\n<p>Warm 2–3 drops between palms, press onto skin and massage upward. Day or night — let the botanicals do the rest.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── SUITABLE FOR ── -->\n<h2>Suitable For</h2>\n<div class=\"suitable-grid\">\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌵</span> <b>Dry &amp; Dehydrated Skin</b> Deeply replenishes moisture-starved skin</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌗</span> <b>Dull Skin</b> Restores natural radiance and brightness</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌑</span> <b>Uneven Skin Tone</b> Rosehip and Kumkumathi gently address pigmentation</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">☀️</span> <b>Day &amp; Night Use</b> Versatile formula — works beautifully morning or evening</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">👰</span> <b>Bridal Glow</b> Begin 6–8 weeks prior for a visible pre-bridal radiance</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌿</span> <b>Normal &amp; Combination Skin</b> Lightweight, non-greasy — balances without overwhelming</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── STORAGE ── -->\n<h2>Storage &amp; Shelf Life</h2>\n<div class=\"storage-row\">\n<div class=\"storage-card\">\n<div class=\"storage-icon\">🏠</div>\n<div>\n<h4>Storage</h4>\n<p>Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. Keep the cap tightly closed after use to preserve the freshness and potency of the botanical oils.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"storage-card\">\n<div class=\"storage-icon\">📅</div>\n<div>\n<h4>Shelf Life</h4>\n<p>24 months from the date of manufacturing. Check the bottom of the bottle for the manufacturing date. Use within 6 months of opening for best results.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── CAUTION ── -->\n<div class=\"caution-block\">⚠️ <b>Caution:</b> For external use only. Avoid direct contact with eyes. If contact occurs, rinse immediately with plenty of clean water. A patch test on a small area of skin is recommended before first full use. Discontinue use if any irritation or sensitivity occurs. Keep out of reach of children.</div>",
