      "id": 7654148014167,
      "title": "Original Kumkumathi Radiance Night  Face Cream",
      "handle": "kumkumadi-nourishing-cream",
      "body_html": "<p><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"> <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Kumkumathi Radiance Night Cream by Kashmir Online Store. Original Ayurvedic night cream with pure Kashmiri Saffron from Pampore, Kumkumathi herb complex, Shea Butter and Vitamin E. Brightens, nourishes and restores skin overnight. 100% natural.\"> <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,600&amp;family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&amp;display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"></p>\n<style>\n  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n\n  body {\n    font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;\n    background: #faf6f0;\n    color: #1c1c1c;\n    line-height: 1.75;\n    padding: 48px 24px;\n    max-width: 800px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  /* ── BRAND ── */\n  .brand-label {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 3px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #b8902a;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── TITLE ── */\n  .product-eyebrow {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-style: italic;\n    color: #9a7a3a;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  h1 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: clamp(30px, 5vw, 52px);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1a0f00;\n    line-height: 1.1;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n  }\n  .product-descriptor {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 17px;\n    font-style: italic;\n    color: #8a6820;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── PILLARS ── */\n  .pillars {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 8px;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n  .pillar {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #1a0f00;\n    border: 1.5px solid #c9a84c;\n    padding: 5px 16px;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── META ROW ── */\n  .meta-row {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 10px;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    margin-bottom: 32px;\n  }\n  .meta-tag {\n    display: inline-flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 7px;\n    background: #fff4e0;\n    border: 1px solid #e8c97a;\n    color: #7a4f00;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    padding: 6px 16px;\n    border-radius: 3px;\n  }\n  .meta-tag.dark {\n    background: #1a0f00;\n    border-color: #1a0f00;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n  }\n\n  /* ── INTRO ── */\n  .intro {\n    font-size: 15.5px;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n    line-height: 1.95;\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\n    padding-left: 18px;\n    border-left: 3px solid #c9a84c;\n  }\n\n  /* ── SECTION HEADING ── */\n  h2 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 26px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1a0f00;\n    margin: 44px 0 16px;\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n  }\n\n  /* ── SAFFRON HERO ── */\n  .saffron-hero {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0f00 0%, #2e1800 55%, #3d2208 100%);\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    padding: 36px 32px;\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  .saffron-hero::before {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    top: -60px; right: -60px;\n    width: 220px; height: 220px;\n    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n  }\n  .saffron-hero::after {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: -40px; left: -40px;\n    width: 160px; height: 160px;\n    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.1);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n  }\n  .saffron-hero-label {\n    font-size: 10px;\n    letter-spacing: 3px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.7);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    position: relative; z-index: 2;\n  }\n  .saffron-hero h3 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: clamp(20px, 3vw, 28px);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    line-height: 1.25;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n    position: relative; z-index: 2;\n  }\n  .saffron-hero p {\n    font-size: 14.5px;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);\n    line-height: 1.9;\n    position: relative; z-index: 2;\n    max-width: 620px;\n  }\n  .saffron-facts {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 0;\n    margin-top: 28px;\n    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);\n    padding-top: 22px;\n    position: relative; z-index: 2;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n  }\n  .saffron-fact {\n    flex: 1;\n    min-width: 130px;\n    padding-right: 20px;\n  }\n  .saffron-fact:not(:last-child) {\n    border-right: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);\n    margin-right: 20px;\n  }\n  .saffron-fact-label {\n    font-size: 10px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.6);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 5px;\n  }\n  .saffron-fact-value {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n\n  /* ── BENEFITS ── */\n  .benefits-list { list-style: none; }\n  .benefits-list li {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 18px;\n    padding: 18px 0;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #ede6d4;\n    font-size: 14.5px;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n  }\n  .benefits-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n  .benefit-icon {\n    width: 40px; height: 40px;\n    background: #fff4e0;\n    border: 1px solid #e8c97a;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-size: 18px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    margin-top: 2px;\n  }\n  .benefit-text b {\n    display: block;\n    color: #1a0f00;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── INGREDIENTS ── */\n  .ingredient-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n  }\n  .ingredient-header {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 16px;\n    padding: 20px 24px;\n    background: #1a0f00;\n  }\n  .ingredient-card.star .ingredient-header {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0f00, #3d2208);\n  }\n  .ingredient-card.star .ingredient-header::after {\n    content: '★ Hero Ingredient';\n    font-size: 10px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.8);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    margin-left: auto;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .ingredient-num {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 36px;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.45);\n    line-height: 1;\n    min-width: 36px;\n  }\n  .ingredient-title-wrap h3 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    margin-bottom: 3px;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n  }\n  .ingredient-title-wrap span {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 1.5px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);\n    font-weight: 500;\n  }\n  .ingredient-body {\n    padding: 20px 24px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #4a4a4a;\n    line-height: 1.82;\n  }\n  .ingredient-body b { color: #1a0f00; }\n  .action-tags {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 6px;\n    margin-top: 12px;\n  }\n  .action-tag {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #7a4f00;\n    background: #fff8ee;\n    border: 1px solid #e8c97a;\n    padding: 3px 10px;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── OVERNIGHT SCIENCE BLOCK ── */\n  .overnight-block {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    margin-top: 4px;\n  }\n  .overnight-header {\n    background: #1a0f00;\n    padding: 18px 24px;\n  }\n  .overnight-header h3 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n  }\n  .overnight-header p {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);\n  }\n  .overnight-body {\n    padding: 22px 24px;\n  }\n  .overnight-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 16px;\n  }\n  .overnight-item {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 12px;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n  }\n  .overnight-icon {\n    font-size: 20px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    margin-top: 2px;\n  }\n  .overnight-item h4 {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1a0f00;\n    margin-bottom: 4px;\n    letter-spacing: 0.3px;\n  }\n  .overnight-item p {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #5a5a5a;\n    line-height: 1.65;\n  }\n\n  /* ── DIRECTIONS ── */\n  .directions-block {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    padding: 6px 26px 6px;\n  }\n  .directions-block ol { list-style: none; counter-reset: d; }\n  .directions-block ol li {\n    counter-increment: d;\n    padding: 15px 0 15px 50px;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0e8d5;\n    font-size: 14.5px;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .directions-block ol li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n  .directions-block ol li::before {\n    content: counter(d);\n    position: absolute; left: 0; top: 13px;\n    width: 30px; height: 30px;\n    background: #1a0f00;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    line-height: 30px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n  }\n\n  .pro-tip {\n    margin-top: 18px;\n    padding: 15px 20px;\n    background: #fff4e0;\n    border-left: 3px solid #c9a84c;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #2c1a0e;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n  }\n\n  /* ── NIGHT RITUAL ── */\n  .ritual-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .ritual-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-top: 3px solid #c9a84c;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 20px 14px 18px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .ritual-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; }\n  .ritual-card h4 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1a0f00;\n    margin-bottom: 7px;\n  }\n  .ritual-card p { font-size: 12.5px; color: #5a5a5a; line-height: 1.6; }\n\n  /* ── SUITABLE FOR ── */\n  .suitable-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .suitable-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 18px 14px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #4a4a4a;\n    line-height: 1.55;\n  }\n  .suitable-card .s-icon { font-size: 24px; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }\n  .suitable-card b { display: block; color: #1a0f00; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }\n\n  /* ── CAUTION ── */\n  .caution-block {\n    margin-top: 44px;\n    padding: 16px 20px;\n    background: #fff9f0;\n    border: 1px solid #f0d8a0;\n    border-left: 4px solid #d4a017;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 13.5px;\n    color: #5a3e00;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n  }\n  .caution-block b { color: #3a2800; }\n\n  @media (max-width: 640px) {\n    .ritual-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n    .suitable-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n    .overnight-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    .saffron-facts { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }\n    .saffron-fact:not(:last-child) {\n      border-right: none;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);\n      padding-bottom: 16px;\n      margin-right: 0;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n<!-- ── TITLE ── -->\n<p class=\"brand-label\">Kashmir Online Store · Skincare</p>\n<p class=\"product-eyebrow\">Original Ayurvedic Night Cream</p>\n<h1><br></h1>\n<p class=\"product-descriptor\">\"Wake Up to Radiance — Night After Night\"</p>\n<div class=\"pillars\">\n<span class=\"pillar\">Brightening</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Nourishing</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Overnight Repair</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Ayurvedic</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Natural</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"meta-row\">\n<span class=\"meta-tag\">🌸 Kashmiri Saffron — Pampore, Kashmir</span> <span class=\"meta-tag dark\">🌙 Overnight Radiance Formula</span> <span class=\"meta-tag dark\">Net Qty: 50 g</span>\n</div>\n<!-- ── INTRO ── -->\n<p class=\"intro\">The <strong>Kumkumathi Radiance Night Cream</strong> is an original night cream crafted with <strong>pure Kashmiri Saffron</strong> from the saffron fields of <strong>Pampore, Kashmir</strong>, the time-honoured <strong>Kumkumathi herb complex</strong>, deeply nourishing <strong>Shea Butter</strong>, skin-restoring <strong>Rosehip Oil</strong>, and protective <strong>Vitamin E</strong>. This rich yet lightweight cream is designed to work in harmony with the skin's natural overnight repair cycle — brightening, nourishing, and restoring while you sleep. Every morning, skin looks visibly more radiant, smoother, and deeply rested. Original formula. All natural. Nothing hidden.</p>\n<!-- ── SAFFRON HERO ── -->\n<div class=\"saffron-hero\">\n<p class=\"saffron-hero-label\">★ The Heart of This Formula</p>\n<h3>Kashmiri Saffron from Pampore —<br>Night's Most Precious Brightening Ingredient</h3>\n<p>At the soul of this night cream is <strong>pure Kashmiri Saffron</strong> — sourced directly from the ancient saffron fields of <strong>Pampore</strong>, the saffron heartland of India and the world. Pampore saffron is globally celebrated for its unmatched richness in <strong>crocin, crocetin, and safranal</strong> — the natural compounds responsible for its legendary skin-brightening, tone-evening, and radiance-restoring power. Applied at night, Kashmiri Saffron works at its peak — entering the skin during its natural repair window and delivering a depth of brightening and nourishment that no other ingredient comes close to.</p>\n<div class=\"saffron-facts\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Origin</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">Pampore, Kashmir Valley</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Active Compounds</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">Crocin · Crocetin · Safranal</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Skin Action</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">Brightens · Evens · Glows</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Best Applied</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">At Night — Peak Absorption</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── BENEFITS ── -->\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\n<ul class=\"benefits-list\">\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">✨</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Brightens Skin and Restores Natural Radiance</b> Kashmiri Saffron's crocin compound works overnight to gently brighten the complexion, reduce the appearance of dullness, and deliver a warm, natural luminosity that is visible from the very first morning.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🌗</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Reduces Uneven Skin Tone and Dark Spots</b> The Kumkumathi herb complex and Saffron actives together address areas of pigmentation, uneven tone, and post-blemish marks — gradually restoring a more balanced and harmonious complexion with nightly use.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🌿</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Deeply Nourishes and Softens the Skin</b> Shea Butter and Rosehip Oil penetrate the skin barrier overnight to deliver rich, sustained nourishment — leaving skin noticeably softer, smoother, and more supple by morning.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🔄</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Supports Overnight Skin Repair and Renewal</b> Formulated to align with the skin's natural nocturnal repair cycle. While you sleep, the cream's botanical actives support cell turnover, collagen integrity, and barrier restoration — waking the skin up renewed.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">💧</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Maintains Deep Overnight Hydration</b> Vitamin E and the cream's natural emollient base lock in moisture throughout the night — preventing transepidermal water loss and ensuring the skin wakes up plump, comfortable, and never tight.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🪷</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Improves Overall Skin Health Over Time</b> Consistent nightly use builds cumulative results — progressively brighter tone, reduced dullness, finer texture, and a complexion that looks and feels genuinely healthier week after week.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- ── WHY NIGHT? ── -->\n<h2>Why a Night Cream? The Science of Overnight Skin</h2>\n<div class=\"overnight-block\">\n<div class=\"overnight-header\">\n<h3>Your Skin Works Harder While You Sleep</h3>\n<p>Why nighttime application delivers superior results</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"overnight-body\">\n<div class=\"overnight-grid\">\n<div class=\"overnight-item\">\n<div class=\"overnight-icon\">🔬</div>\n<div>\n<h4>Peak Cell Renewal</h4>\n<p>Skin cell turnover rate increases significantly between 11 PM and 4 AM — the ideal window for botanical actives to support renewal and repair.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"overnight-item\">\n<div class=\"overnight-icon\">💧</div>\n<div>\n<h4>Deeper Absorption</h4>\n<p>With no environmental stressors, UV exposure, or makeup on the skin, ingredients penetrate deeper and work uninterrupted for full hours.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"overnight-item\">\n<div class=\"overnight-icon\">🌡️</div>\n<div>\n<h4>Higher Skin Temperature</h4>\n<p>Body temperature rises slightly during sleep — warming the skin and naturally increasing blood circulation for enhanced nutrient delivery to cells.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"overnight-item\">\n<div class=\"overnight-icon\">✨</div>\n<div>\n<h4>Saffron at Its Best</h4>\n<p>Kashmiri Saffron's brightening compounds are most effective when given undisturbed overnight time — which is exactly what this cream provides.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── KEY INGREDIENTS ── -->\n<h2>Key Ingredients</h2>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card star\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">01</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Kashmiri Saffron — Pampore, Kashmir</h3>\n<span>Pure · Hand-Harvested · Hero Ingredient</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">Sourced exclusively from <b>Pampore, Kashmir</b> — the saffron capital of India. Pure Kashmiri Saffron is the most important ingredient in this night cream. Rich in <b>crocin, crocetin, and safranal</b>, it brightens the complexion, reduces melanin overproduction behind dark spots and uneven skin tone, and restores natural luminosity overnight. No other ingredient does what Kashmiri Saffron does — and nothing replaces the real thing.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Brightening</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Tone Evening</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Radiance</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Dark Spot Reduction</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">02</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Kumkumathi Herb Complex</h3>\n<span>Traditional Ayurvedic Brightening Blend</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">The original Kumkumathi formulation — an Ayurvedic heritage blend of herbs, resins, and botanical extracts traditionally used in Indian beauty rituals to nourish skin, improve complexion, and restore natural glow. Paired with Kashmiri Saffron, this complex forms the most powerful brightening combination at the heart of this cream.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Herbal Brightening</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Complexion Improving</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Ayurvedic Heritage</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">03</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Shea Butter</h3>\n<span>Rich Overnight Nourishing Emollient</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">Pure <b>Shea Butter</b> is an exceptionally rich natural emollient that melts into the skin, delivering deep overnight moisture and nourishment. Packed with fatty acids, vitamins A and E, and natural anti-inflammatory compounds — it softens rough texture, soothes stressed skin, and forms the lush, creamy base that makes this night cream feel truly luxurious.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Deep Moisture</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Skin Softening</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Soothing</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Nourishing</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">04</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Rosehip Oil</h3>\n<span>Vitamin A &amp; C Rich Regenerating Oil</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">Cold-pressed from rosehip seeds and naturally rich in <b>Vitamin A (retinol precursor)</b>, <b>Vitamin C</b>, and essential fatty acids. Rosehip Oil is one of the most effective natural ingredients for overnight skin renewal — visibly reducing dark spots, improving skin texture, and supporting firmer, brighter skin with consistent use.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Cell Renewal</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Firming</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Brightening</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Texture Improving</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">05</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Vitamin E</h3>\n<span>Antioxidant Skin Protector &amp; Stabiliser</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">\n<b>Pure Vitamin E (Tocopherol)</b> protects the skin from oxidative stress, supports the overnight repair process, and significantly improves moisture retention. It also preserves the freshness and stability of the botanical ingredients in this cream — ensuring every use is as potent as the first.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Antioxidant</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Moisture Retention</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Repair Support</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── DIRECTIONS ── -->\n<h2>Directions for Use</h2>\n<div class=\"directions-block\">\n<ol>\n<li>Begin your night routine with a thoroughly cleansed face and neck — free from makeup and impurities.</li>\n<li>If using a toner or face mist, apply it first and allow it to be absorbed.</li>\n<li>If using a serum, apply your serum and allow it to absorb fully before the cream.</li>\n<li>Take a small amount of Kumkumathi Radiance Night Cream — about the size of a pea — onto your fingertips.</li>\n<li>Apply to the face and neck in gentle upward circular motions, covering all areas evenly.</li>\n<li>Leave on overnight. Do not rinse. Allow the cream to work fully through the night.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pro-tip\">🌙 <strong>For Best Results:</strong> Use every night without skipping. The brightening and nourishing benefits of Kashmiri Saffron and the Kumkumathi herb complex build cumulatively — consistent nightly use over 4–6 weeks delivers the most visible and lasting transformation in skin radiance and texture.</div>\n<!-- ── NIGHT RITUAL ── -->\n<h2>Your Complete Night Ritual</h2>\n<div class=\"ritual-grid\">\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">🧖</div>\n<h4>1 — Cleanse</h4>\n<p>Gentle natural cleanser to remove all makeup and impurities.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">💧</div>\n<h4>2 — Tone</h4>\n<p>Rose water or natural toner to balance and prep the skin.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">🌿</div>\n<h4>3 — Serum</h4>\n<p>Apply your serum. Allow to fully absorb before cream.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">🌙</div>\n<h4>4 — Night Cream</h4>\n<p>Apply Kumkumathi Radiance Night Cream and let saffron restore overnight.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── SUITABLE FOR ── -->\n<h2>Suitable For</h2>\n<div class=\"suitable-grid\">\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌗</span> <b>Dull Skin</b> Restores glow and radiance lost to fatigue and stress</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌑</span> <b>Uneven Skin Tone</b> Gently targets dark spots and pigmentation over time</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌵</span> <b>Dry &amp; Dehydrated Skin</b> Deeply nourishes and restores overnight moisture</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🕐</span> <b>All Ages</b> Beneficial from early 20s onwards for radiance maintenance</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">👰</span> <b>Bridal Skincare</b> Begin 6–8 weeks prior for a deep pre-bridal glow transformation</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌿</span> <b>Normal, Dry &amp; Combination</b> Balanced natural formula suitable for most skin types</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── CAUTION ── -->\n<div class=\"caution-block\">⚠️ <b>Caution:</b> For external use only. Avoid direct contact with eyes. If contact occurs, rinse immediately with plenty of clean water. Perform a patch test on a small skin area before first full use, especially for sensitive skin. Discontinue use if any irritation or discomfort occurs. Keep out of reach of children. Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight.</div>",
