  }\n  .ingredient-card.star .ingredient-header {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1000, #3d2a08);\n  }\n  .ingredient-card.star .ingredient-header::after {\n    content: '★ Hero Ingredient';\n    font-size: 10px;\n    letter-spacing: 2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.8);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    margin-left: auto;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .ingredient-num {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 36px;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.45);\n    line-height: 1;\n    min-width: 36px;\n  }\n  .ingredient-title-wrap h3 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    margin-bottom: 3px;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n  }\n  .ingredient-title-wrap span {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 1.5px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);\n    font-weight: 500;\n  }\n  .ingredient-body {\n    padding: 20px 24px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #4a4a4a;\n    line-height: 1.82;\n  }\n  .ingredient-body b { color: #1a1000; }\n  .action-tags {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 6px;\n    margin-top: 12px;\n  }\n  .action-tag {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #7a4f00;\n    background: #fff8ee;\n    border: 1px solid #e8c97a;\n    padding: 3px 10px;\n    border-radius: 2px;\n  }\n\n  /* ── DIRECTIONS ── */\n  .directions-block {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    padding: 6px 26px 6px;\n  }\n  .directions-block ol { list-style: none; counter-reset: d; }\n  .directions-block ol li {\n    counter-increment: d;\n    padding: 15px 0 15px 50px;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0e8d5;\n    font-size: 14.5px;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .directions-block ol li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n  .directions-block ol li::before {\n    content: counter(d);\n    position: absolute; left: 0; top: 13px;\n    width: 30px; height: 30px;\n    background: #1a1000;\n    color: #e2c47a;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    line-height: 30px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n  }\n\n  .pro-tip {\n    margin-top: 18px;\n    padding: 15px 20px;\n    background: #fff4e0;\n    border-left: 3px solid #c9a84c;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #2c1a0e;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n  }\n\n  /* ── SUITABLE FOR ── */\n  .suitable-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .suitable-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 18px 14px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #4a4a4a;\n    line-height: 1.55;\n  }\n  .suitable-card .s-icon { font-size: 24px; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }\n  .suitable-card b { display: block; color: #1a1000; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }\n\n  /* ── STORAGE ── */\n  .storage-row {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 12px;\n  }\n  .storage-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 18px 20px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 14px;\n  }\n  .storage-icon { font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }\n  .storage-card h4 {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 1.5px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #9a9a9a;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 6px;\n  }\n  .storage-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #3a3a3a; line-height: 1.65; }\n\n  /* ── CAUTION ── */\n  .caution-block {\n    margin-top: 44px;\n    padding: 16px 20px;\n    background: #fff9f0;\n    border: 1px solid #f0d8a0;\n    border-left: 4px solid #d4a017;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 13.5px;\n    color: #5a3e00;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n  }\n  .caution-block b { color: #3a2800; }\n\n  @media (max-width: 600px) {\n    .protection-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    .suitable-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n    .storage-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    .saffron-facts { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }\n    .saffron-fact:not(:last-child) {\n      border-right: none;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15);\n      padding-bottom: 16px;\n      margin-right: 0;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n<!-- ── TITLE ── -->\n<p class=\"brand-label\">Kashmir Online Store · Sun Care</p>\n<p class=\"product-descriptor\">\"Shield Your Glow — Protect, Nourish, Radiate\"</p>\n<div class=\"spf-badge-row\">\n<div class=\"spf-badge\">SPF 50<sup>+</sup>\n</div>\n<div class=\"spf-sub\">Broad Spectrum Protection<br>UVA &amp; UVB Defence</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pillars\">\n<span class=\"pillar\">Sun Protection</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Anti-Tanning</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Skin Brightening</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Hydrating</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Lightweight</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"meta-row\">\n<span class=\"meta-tag\">🌸 Kashmiri Saffron Extract</span> <span class=\"meta-tag dark\">SPF 50+</span> <span class=\"meta-tag green\">✦ No Synthetic Additives</span>\n</div>\n<!-- ── INTRO ── -->\n<p class=\"intro\">The <strong>Saffron Protective Sunscreen SPF 50+</strong> by <strong>Kashmir Online Store</strong> is a lightweight, natural sunscreen enriched with <strong>pure Kashmiri Saffron extract</strong>, <strong>Zinc Oxide</strong>, <strong>Sun Boosters</strong>, <strong>Vitamin E</strong>, and <strong>skin conditioning agents</strong>. It delivers <strong>broad spectrum SPF 50+ protection</strong> against harmful UVA and UVB rays while simultaneously brightening the skin, maintaining hydration, and supporting a naturally radiant complexion throughout the day. A sunscreen that does far more than protect — it nourishes and glows with every application.</p>\n<!-- ── PROTECTION STATS ── -->\n<h2>Protection at a Glance</h2>\n<div class=\"protection-row\">\n<div class=\"protection-card\">\n<div class=\"protection-value\">50<sup>+</sup>\n</div>\n<div class=\"protection-label\">SPF Rating</div>\n<div class=\"protection-desc\">Blocks over 98% of UVB rays that cause sunburn and sun damage</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"protection-card\">\n<div class=\"protection-value\">PA<sup>+++</sup>\n</div>\n<div class=\"protection-label\">UVA Protection</div>\n<div class=\"protection-desc\">High-grade UVA defence against tanning, ageing, and deep skin damage</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"protection-card\">\n<div class=\"protection-value\">2–3<sup>hr</sup>\n</div>\n<div class=\"protection-label\">Reapply Every</div>\n<div class=\"protection-desc\">Reapply every 2–3 hours outdoors for continuous full protection</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── SAFFRON HERO ── -->\n<div class=\"saffron-hero\" style=\"margin-top: 44px;\">\n<p class=\"saffron-hero-label\">★ The Difference in This Sunscreen</p>\n<h3>Kashmiri Saffron Extract —<br>Protection That Also Brightens</h3>\n<p>Most sunscreens protect — this one protects <em>and</em> brightens. The secret is <strong>pure Kashmiri Saffron extract</strong> — sourced from the legendary saffron fields of <strong>Pampore, Kashmir</strong>. While Zinc Oxide shields the skin from UV damage, Kashmiri Saffron's <strong>crocin and safranal compounds</strong> work simultaneously to brighten the complexion, even skin tone, and counter the dullness and discolouration that prolonged sun exposure causes. The result is skin that is not just protected — but visibly more radiant and nourished with every use.</p>\n<div class=\"saffron-facts\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Origin</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">Pampore, Kashmir</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Active Compounds</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">Crocin · Safranal</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Skin Benefit</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">Brightens · Evens · Protects</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact\">\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-label\">Formula</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-fact-value\">Natural · No Synthetics</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── BENEFITS ── -->\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\n<ul class=\"benefits-list\">\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🛡️</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Helps Protect Skin from Sun Damage and Environmental Stress</b> Zinc Oxide forms a natural mineral barrier on the skin's surface that reflects and scatters UVA and UVB rays — preventing the sun damage, inflammation, and oxidative stress that accumulates with daily unprotected exposure.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🌗</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Helps Prevent Tanning Caused by Sun Exposure</b> Broad spectrum SPF 50+ protection minimises melanin overproduction triggered by UV exposure — helping prevent the darkening, patchy tanning, and uneven tone that builds up without daily sun protection.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">💧</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Maintains Skin Hydration and Softness</b> Skin conditioning agents and Vitamin E keep the skin barrier hydrated and comfortable through the day — no tight, dry, or chalky feeling common to many sunscreens. Skin stays soft, smooth, and nourished under the sun.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">✨</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Supports Brighter and Healthier-Looking Skin</b> Kashmiri Saffron extract works alongside the protective formula to brighten the complexion, reduce dullness caused by sun exposure, and maintain the natural radiance of the skin throughout the day.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🌿</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Lightweight Formula Suitable for Daily Use</b> Despite its rich protective profile, this sunscreen spreads easily and absorbs without heaviness — making it genuinely comfortable for daily use under makeup, outdoors, or on its own.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- ── KEY INGREDIENTS ── -->\n<h2>Key Ingredients</h2>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card star\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">01</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Kashmiri Saffron Extract</h3>\n<span>Pampore, Kashmir · Brightening Hero</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">\n<b>Pure Kashmiri Saffron extract</b> sourced from Pampore — the most celebrated saffron-producing region in the world. In this sunscreen, Saffron's <b>crocin and safranal</b> compounds serve a dual role: they brighten and even the skin tone while counteracting the dullness and discolouration that UV exposure causes over time. A sunscreen ingredient that protects and actively improves the complexion simultaneously.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Brightening</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Tone Evening</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Anti-Dullness</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Radiance</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">02</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Zinc Oxide</h3>\n<span>Natural Mineral Broad Spectrum UV Filter</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">\n<b>Zinc Oxide</b> is a natural mineral sunscreen agent that sits on the skin's surface and physically reflects and scatters both UVA and UVB radiation. Unlike synthetic UV filters, Zinc Oxide provides broad spectrum protection through a natural mineral mechanism — making it gentle on the skin and suitable for sensitive skin types. It is the protective backbone of this formulation.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">UVA Protection</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">UVB Protection</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Broad Spectrum</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Mineral Filter</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">03</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Sun Boosters</h3>\n<span>Natural SPF-Enhancing Botanical Complex</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">A blend of <b>plant-derived botanical compounds</b> that work alongside Zinc Oxide to enhance and extend sun protection performance. These natural sun boosters help improve the uniformity of UV coverage across the skin surface, ensuring consistent broad spectrum protection through all outdoor conditions throughout the day.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">SPF Enhancement</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">UV Coverage</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Botanical</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">04</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Vitamin E</h3>\n<span>Antioxidant Sun Damage Defence</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">\n<b>Vitamin E (Tocopherol)</b> plays a vital role in a sunscreen formula — it neutralises the free radicals generated by UV exposure that cause oxidative skin damage, premature ageing, and post-sun dullness. It also deeply conditions the skin, improves moisture retention, and supports overall skin health under sun stress.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Free Radical Defence</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Antioxidant</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Skin Conditioning</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Anti-Ageing</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">05</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Skin Conditioning Agents</h3>\n<span>Hydrating &amp; Texture Smoothing Complex</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">A blend of <b>natural skin conditioning agents</b> that give this sunscreen its lightweight, comfortable texture. They ensure the formula spreads evenly across the skin, maintains skin hydration throughout the day, and leaves behind a smooth, soft finish — free of the chalky residue or white cast associated with many mineral sunscreens.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Hydrating</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Smooth Texture</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">No White Cast</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Comfortable Wear</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── DIRECTIONS ── -->\n<h2>Directions for Use</h2>\n<div class=\"directions-block\">\n<ol>\n<li>Apply the sunscreen generously and evenly to the face and all exposed areas of skin.</li>\n<li>Apply at least <strong>15 minutes before going outdoors</strong> to allow the mineral filter to form a complete protective layer.</li>\n<li>Ensure full coverage including the neck, ears, and any other sun-exposed areas.</li>\n<li>When outdoors, <strong>reapply every 2–3 hours</strong> — more frequently if swimming, sweating, or towel-drying.</li>\n<li>For daily indoor use, one application in the morning is sufficient as part of your skincare routine.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pro-tip\">☀️ <strong>Important:</strong> No sunscreen provides 100% protection. For extended outdoor exposure, combine this sunscreen with protective clothing, hats, and shade where possible. Consistent daily use — even on cloudy days — is the most effective way to prevent cumulative sun damage and maintain even skin tone over time.</div>\n<!-- ── SUITABLE FOR ── -->\n<h2>Suitable For</h2>\n<div class=\"suitable-grid\">\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">☀️</span> <b>Daily Outdoor Use</b> Trusted broad spectrum protection for all daily activities</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌗</span> <b>Tanning-Prone Skin</b> Helps prevent UV-triggered melanin overproduction</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">✨</span> <b>Dull Skin</b> Saffron actively brightens while Zinc Oxide protects</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">👤</span> <b>All Skin Types</b> Lightweight and suitable for normal, dry and oily skin</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">💄</span> <b>Under Makeup</b> Smooth base that wears comfortably under any foundation</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌿</span> <b>Sensitive Skin</b> Mineral Zinc Oxide is naturally gentle — no synthetic filters</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── STORAGE ── -->\n<h2>Storage &amp; Shelf Life</h2>\n<div class=\"storage-row\">\n<div class=\"storage-card\">\n<div class=\"storage-icon\">🏠</div>\n<div>\n<h4>Storage</h4>\n<p>Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat. Keep the cap tightly closed after use to preserve the integrity of the SPF filter and natural ingredients.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"storage-card\">\n<div class=\"storage-icon\">📅</div>\n<div>\n<h4>Shelf Life</h4>\n<p>24 months from the date of manufacturing. Check the packaging for the manufacturing date. Once opened, use within 12 months for best SPF efficacy.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── CAUTION ── -->\n<div class=\"caution-block\">⚠️ <b>Caution:</b> For external use only. Avoid direct contact with eyes. If contact occurs, rinse immediately and thoroughly with clean water. Discontinue use immediately if any irritation, redness, or sensitivity occurs. Perform a patch test before first full use if you have sensitive skin. Keep out of reach of children. Do not use on broken or damaged skin.</div>",
