;\n  }\n  .ritual-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; }\n  .ritual-card h4 {\n    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    color: #1a0c00;\n    margin-bottom: 7px;\n  }\n  .ritual-card p { font-size: 12.5px; color: #5a5a5a; line-height: 1.6; }\n\n  /* ── SUITABLE FOR ── */\n  .suitable-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .suitable-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 18px 14px;\n    text-align: center;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #4a4a4a;\n    line-height: 1.55;\n  }\n  .suitable-card .s-icon { font-size: 24px; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }\n  .suitable-card b { display: block; color: #1a0c00; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }\n\n  /* ── FEATURES & SPECS ── */\n  .specs-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14px; }\n  .specs-table tr { border-bottom: 1px solid #ede6d4; }\n  .specs-table tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n  .specs-table td {\n    padding: 13px 16px;\n    vertical-align: top;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    color: #3a3a3a;\n  }\n  .specs-table td:first-child {\n    font-size: 12px;\n    letter-spacing: 1px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #7a7a7a;\n    width: 36%;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  }\n\n  /* ── STORAGE ── */\n  .storage-row {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    gap: 12px;\n  }\n  .storage-card {\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid #e8dfc8;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    padding: 18px 20px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 14px;\n  }\n  .storage-icon { font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }\n  .storage-card h4 {\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 1.5px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #9a9a9a;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin-bottom: 6px;\n  }\n  .storage-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #3a3a3a; line-height: 1.65; }\n\n  /* ── CAUTION ── */\n  .caution-block {\n    margin-top: 44px;\n    padding: 16px 20px;\n    background: #fff9f0;\n    border: 1px solid #f0d8a0;\n    border-left: 4px solid #d4a017;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 13.5px;\n    color: #5a3e00;\n    line-height: 1.78;\n  }\n  .caution-block b { color: #3a2800; }\n\n  @media (max-width: 640px) {\n    .saffron-compounds { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    .saffron-origin-strip { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }\n    .origin-item:not(:last-child) { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); padding-bottom: 16px; margin-right: 0; }\n    .ritual-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n    .suitable-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }\n    .storage-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n  }\n</style>\n<!-- ── TITLE ── -->\n<div class=\"pillars\">\n<span class=\"pillar\">Brightening</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Radiance</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Nourishing</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Glow</span> <span class=\"pillar\">Ayurvedic</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"meta-row\">\n<span class=\"meta-tag\">🌸 Pure Kashmiri Saffron — Pampore, Kashmir</span> <span class=\"meta-tag dark\">Net Qty: 20 ml</span> <span class=\"meta-tag dark\">AM &amp; PM · Daily Use</span>\n</div>\n<!-- ── INTRO ── -->\n<p class=\"intro\">The <strong>Pure Kashmiri Saffron Serum</strong> by <strong>Kashmir Online Store</strong> is an original saffron-first facial serum built around the highest-grade <strong>Kashmiri Saffron extract</strong> from the legendary fields of <strong>Pampore, Kashmir</strong> — enriched with <strong>Vitamin C</strong>, <strong>Hyaluronic Acid</strong>, <strong>Niacinamide</strong>, <strong>Vitamin E</strong>, and a <strong>Botanical Oil Complex</strong>. This 20 ml concentrated serum delivers the full brightening, nourishing, and skin-restoring power of real Kashmiri Saffron — in a lightweight, fast-absorbing formula that transforms the complexion with consistent daily use. Authentic. Pure. Nothing hidden.</p>\n<!-- ── SAFFRON FULL HERO ── -->\n<div class=\"saffron-full\">\n<p class=\"saffron-full-label\">🌸 The Soul of This Serum</p>\n<h3>Pure Kashmiri Saffron from Pampore —<br>The World's Most Precious Skin Ingredient</h3>\n<p>There is saffron — and then there is <strong>Kashmiri Saffron from Pampore</strong>. The saffron fields of Pampore in the Kashmir Valley produce what is globally recognised as the finest, most potent saffron on earth. Grown at altitude in Kashmir's unique climate, hand-harvested at the precise peak of bloom, and processed with care to preserve every active compound — Pampore saffron carries a concentration of skin-active molecules that no other saffron origin matches.</p>\n<p>In skincare, Kashmiri Saffron has been treasured for thousands of years — used by royalty and passed through generations as the ultimate skin brightener. Modern extraction science now allows us to concentrate these benefits into a serum where every drop delivers the full power of crocin, crocetin, and safranal directly to your skin.</p>\n<div class=\"saffron-compounds\">\n<div class=\"compound-card\">\n<div class=\"compound-name\">Crocin</div>\n<div class=\"compound-role\">Primary brightening compound — reduces melanin and evens skin tone</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"compound-card\">\n<div class=\"compound-name\">Crocetin</div>\n<div class=\"compound-role\">Improves skin oxygenation, cellular repair and radiance from within</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"compound-card\">\n<div class=\"compound-name\">Safranal</div>\n<div class=\"compound-role\">Antioxidant and anti-inflammatory — protects and soothes the skin</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"saffron-origin-strip\">\n<div class=\"origin-item\">\n<div class=\"origin-label\">Origin</div>\n<div class=\"origin-value\">Pampore, Kashmir Valley</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"origin-item\">\n<div class=\"origin-label\">Harvest</div>\n<div class=\"origin-value\">Hand-Picked at Peak Bloom</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"origin-item\">\n<div class=\"origin-label\">Grade</div>\n<div class=\"origin-value\">Pure · Premium Grade</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"origin-item\">\n<div class=\"origin-label\">Key Action</div>\n<div class=\"origin-value\">Brightens · Evens · Glows</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── BENEFITS ── -->\n<h2>Benefits</h2>\n<ul class=\"benefits-list\">\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">✨</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Brightens Complexion and Restores Natural Radiance</b> Kashmiri Saffron's crocin and Vitamin C work together to reduce melanin overproduction, fade dark spots, and deliver a warm, luminous brightness that builds with every use — the kind of natural glow that comes from healthy, well-nourished skin.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🌗</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Reduces Uneven Skin Tone and Dullness</b> The concentrated saffron extract targets areas of uneven pigmentation, sun-induced discolouration, and post-blemish marks — gradually bringing the complexion back to a more even, balanced, and harmonious tone over consistent daily use.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">💧</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Deeply Hydrates and Plumps the Skin</b> Hyaluronic Acid penetrates across multiple skin layers to fill moisture reservoirs — visibly plumping the skin, softening fine lines, and maintaining the dewy, hydrated base that truly radiant skin requires.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🛡️</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Protects Skin from Oxidative Stress</b> Safranal and Vitamin E are powerful antioxidants that neutralise the free radicals generated by UV exposure, pollution, and daily environmental stress — protecting the skin's health and preventing the premature dullness and ageing they cause.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🪷</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Nourishes and Improves Overall Skin Texture</b> The Botanical Oil Complex and Niacinamide work together to refine skin texture, strengthen the moisture barrier, and deliver deep botanical nourishment — leaving skin visibly smoother, softer, and more supple with every application.</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"benefit-icon\">🔄</div>\n<div class=\"benefit-text\">\n<b>Supports Skin Renewal and Healthy Complexion Over Time</b> Crocetin improves cellular oxygenation and supports natural skin cell renewal — meaning the skin not just looks better on the surface but becomes healthier, more resilient, and more luminous from within with regular use.</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- ── KEY INGREDIENTS ── -->\n<h2>Key Ingredients</h2>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card star\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">01</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Kashmiri Saffron Extract</h3>\n<span>Pampore, Kashmir · Pure · Hand-Harvested</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">The foundation and soul of this entire serum. <b>Pure Kashmiri Saffron extract</b> from Pampore — the undisputed finest saffron origin in the world. Every drop of this serum carries a concentrated dose of <b>crocin</b> (brightening), <b>crocetin</b> (renewal and oxygenation), and <b>safranal</b> (antioxidant and soothing). Used daily, these saffron actives progressively brighten the complexion, reduce pigmentation, restore radiance, and improve the overall health and vitality of the skin in a way that no other single ingredient achieves.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Brightening</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Tone Evening</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Radiance</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Antioxidant</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Skin Renewal</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">02</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Vitamin C</h3>\n<span>Brightening &amp; Collagen Supporting Antioxidant</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">\n<b>Vitamin C (Ascorbic Acid)</b> is one of the most powerful natural brightening and antioxidant actives for the skin. In this serum, it pairs perfectly with Kashmiri Saffron — both targeting pigmentation through different mechanisms for a synergistic brightening effect that is stronger than either ingredient alone. It also supports natural collagen synthesis for firmer, more resilient skin over time.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Brightening Synergy</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Collagen Support</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Antioxidant</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">03</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Hyaluronic Acid</h3>\n<span>Multi-Depth Hydration Active</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">\n<b>Hyaluronic Acid</b> works across multiple molecular weights to hydrate all layers of the skin simultaneously — drawing in moisture, maintaining plumpness, and creating the dewy, hydrated base that allows saffron's brightening compounds to work at their absolute best. Radiance on dry skin is dull; radiance on hydrated skin is luminous.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Deep Hydration</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Plumping</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Elasticity</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">04</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Niacinamide</h3>\n<span>Vitamin B3 · Tone &amp; Texture Perfector</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">\n<b>Niacinamide</b> completes the brightening trio alongside Kashmiri Saffron and Vitamin C — inhibiting melanin transfer to the skin surface, refining pores, and strengthening the skin barrier. It ensures that as saffron brightens, the skin stays smooth, even, and resilient underneath.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Tone Correcting</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Pore Refining</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Barrier Strengthening</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-card\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-header\">\n<div class=\"ingredient-num\">05</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-title-wrap\">\n<h3>Vitamin E &amp; Botanical Oil Complex</h3>\n<span>Antioxidant Protection &amp; Nourishing Base</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ingredient-body\">\n<b>Vitamin E</b> shields the skin from oxidative damage and supports the overnight repair cycle — while the <b>Botanical Oil Complex</b> delivers deep nourishment, improves skin texture, and gives the serum its soft, non-greasy, skin-loving feel. Together they ensure every application leaves skin not just brighter but genuinely healthier.\n<div class=\"action-tags\">\n<span class=\"action-tag\">Antioxidant</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Nourishing</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Skin Softening</span> <span class=\"action-tag\">Repair Support</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── RESULTS ── -->\n<h2>Before &amp; After — What to Expect</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Timeline</th>\n<th>Visible Skin Change</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Day 1–3</td>\n<td>Skin feels immediately more hydrated, soft, and nourished. A subtle warmth and luminosity is noticeable from the first few uses.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Week 1–2</td>\n<td>Dullness visibly reduces. Skin tone begins to look more even and alive. Surface texture improves noticeably in smoothness.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Week 3–4</td>\n<td>Dark spots and pigmentation begin to fade. Skin tone becomes significantly more even. Natural glow is clearly visible day-to-day.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Week 5–6</td>\n<td>Visibly brighter, more radiant complexion. Fine lines appear softer. Skin looks genuinely healthy, plump, and luminous.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Week 8+</td>\n<td>Peak results — transformed complexion with even tone, deep radiance, and the kind of lit-from-within glow that is the true signature of Kashmiri Saffron.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- ── DIRECTIONS ── -->\n<h2>Directions for Use</h2>\n<div class=\"directions-block\">\n<ol>\n<li>Begin with a thoroughly cleansed face and neck — remove all makeup and impurities completely.</li>\n<li>Dispense 2–3 drops of the Pure Kashmiri Saffron Serum onto your fingertips. For this 20 ml bottle, 2 drops is sufficient for full face and neck coverage.</li>\n<li>Apply to the face and neck, pressing gently into the skin and massaging in upward circular motions until fully absorbed.</li>\n<li>Follow immediately with your moisturiser to seal in the serum's active benefits and enhance the glow finish.</li>\n<li>Use morning and night consistently. The brightening and nourishing benefits of Kashmiri Saffron build cumulatively — daily, uninterrupted use delivers the most visible and lasting transformation.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"pro-tip\">🌙 <strong>Night Use Maximises Results:</strong> While this serum works beautifully in the morning, the real transformation happens overnight. Kashmiri Saffron's crocin and crocetin work most intensively during the skin's natural nighttime repair cycle — apply nightly before bed for accelerated brightening, renewal, and the most visible morning glow.</div>\n<!-- ── RITUAL ── -->\n<h2>Your Daily Saffron Ritual</h2>\n<div class=\"ritual-grid\">\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">🧖</div>\n<h4>1 — Cleanse</h4>\n<p>Natural gentle cleanser. Fully remove makeup and impurities before application.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">🌿</div>\n<h4>2 — Tone</h4>\n<p>Rose water or natural toner. Apply to damp skin for deeper serum absorption.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">🌸</div>\n<h4>3 — Saffron Serum</h4>\n<p>2–3 drops. Press and massage gently. 60 seconds to fully absorb.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ritual-card\">\n<div class=\"ritual-icon\">💧</div>\n<h4>4 — Moisturise</h4>\n<p>Seal the serum with moisturiser to lock in radiance and maximise glow.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── SUITABLE FOR ── -->\n<h2>Suitable For</h2>\n<div class=\"suitable-grid\">\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌗</span> <b>Dull Skin</b> Restores natural radiance from the very first week</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌑</span> <b>Uneven Skin Tone</b> Crocin targets pigmentation and dark spots directly</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌵</span> <b>Dry Skin</b> Hyaluronic Acid deeply restores lost moisture</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">☀️</span> <b>AM &amp; PM</b> Lightweight formula — suitable for day and night</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">👰</span> <b>Bridal Glow</b> Begin 6–8 weeks prior for peak pre-bridal radiance</div>\n<div class=\"suitable-card\">\n<span class=\"s-icon\">🌿</span> <b>All Skin Types</b> Balanced natural formula for normal, dry and combination skin</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── FEATURES & SPECS ── -->\n<h2>Features &amp; Specs</h2>\n<table class=\"specs-table\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Product Type</td>\n<td>Face Serum — Leave-In</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Net Quantity</td>\n<td>20 ml</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Texture</td>\n<td>Lightweight, fast-absorbing oil serum</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Finish</td>\n<td>Radiant, luminous, non-greasy</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Hero Ingredient</td>\n<td>Kashmiri Saffron Extract — Pampore, Kashmir</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Key Actives</td>\n<td>Crocin, Crocetin, Safranal, Vitamin C, Hyaluronic Acid, Niacinamide</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Suitable For</td>\n<td>All skin types — normal, dry, combination</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>When to Use</td>\n<td>Morning and night — after cleansing, before moisturiser</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Formula</td>\n<td>100% Natural · Cruelty-Free · No Synthetic Additives</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Shelf Life</td>\n<td>24 months from manufacturing date</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- ── STORAGE ── -->\n<h2>Storage &amp; Shelf Life</h2>\n<div class=\"storage-row\">\n<div class=\"storage-card\">\n<div class=\"storage-icon\">🏠</div>\n<div>\n<h4>Storage</h4>\n<p>Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat. Keep the dropper cap tightly closed after every use to preserve the potency of the saffron extract and Vitamin C.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"storage-card\">\n<div class=\"storage-icon\">📅</div>\n<div>\n<h4>Shelf Life</h4>\n<p>24 months from the date of manufacturing. Check the packaging for the manufacturing date. Use within 6 months of opening for peak active performance.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- ── CAUTION ── -->\n<div class=\"caution-block\">⚠️ <b>Caution:</b> For external use only. Avoid direct contact with eyes. If contact occurs, rinse immediately and thoroughly with clean water. A patch test on a small skin area is recommended before first full use. Discontinue use if any irritation or sensitivity occurs. Keep out of reach of children. Store away from direct sunlight to preserve saffron extract potency.</div>",
